    { 10  ;   ;Salespers./Purch. Code;Code20      ;TableRelation=Salesperson/Purchaser.Code;
                                                   OnValidate=VAR
                                                                UserSetup@1000 : Record 91;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                IF "Salespers./Purch. Code" <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                                                  UserSetup.SETCURRENTKEY("Salespers./Purch. Code");
                                                                  UserSetup.SETRANGE("Salespers./Purch. Code","Salespers./Purch. Code");
                                                                  IF UserSetup.FINDFIRST THEN
                                                                    ERROR(Text001,"Salespers./Purch. Code",UserSetup."User ID");
                                                                END;
                                                              END;

                                                   ValidateTableRelation=No;
                                                   TestTableRelation=No;
                                                   CaptionML=ENU=Salespers./Purch. Code }
    { 11  ;   ;Approver ID         ;Code50        ;TableRelation="User Setup"."User ID";
                                                   OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                IF "Approver ID" = "User ID" THEN
                                                                  FIELDERROR("Approver ID");
                                                              END;

                                                   OnLookup=VAR
                                                              UserSetup@1000 : Record 91;
                                                            BEGIN
                                                              UserSetup.SETFILTER("User ID",'<>%1',"User ID");
                                                              IF PAGE.RUNMODAL(PAGE::"Approval User Setup",UserSetup) = ACTION::LookupOK THEN
                                                                VALIDATE("Approver ID",UserSetup."User ID");
                                                            END;

                                                   CaptionML=ENU=Approver ID }
    { 12  ;   ;Sales Amount Approval Limit;Integer;OnValidate=BEGIN

                                                   CaptionML=ENU=Sales Resp. Ctr. Filter }
    { 5701;   ;Purchase Resp. Ctr. Filter;Code10  ;TableRelation="Responsibility Center";
                                                   OnValidate=VAR
                                                                PurchHeader@1001 : Record 38;
                                                                PurchLine@1002 : Record 39;
                                                                RespCtr@1000 : Record 5714;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                // PHP Start
                                                                IF ("Purchase Resp. Ctr. Filter" <> '') AND (xRec."Purchase Resp. Ctr. Filter" <> '')  AND (RespCtr.GET("Purchase Resp. Ctr. Filter")) THEN BEGIN
                                                                  PurchHeader.SETRANGE("Responsibility Center", xRec."Purchase Resp. Ctr. Filter");
                                                                  PurchHeader.SETRANGE("Request Type", PurchHeader."Request Type"::" ");
                                                                  IF PurchHeader.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
                                                                    REPEAT
                                                                      PurchHeader."Responsibility Center" := RespCtr.Code;
                                                                      PurchHeader.MODIFY;
                                                                      PurchLine.SETRANGE("Document No.", PurchHeader."No.");
                                                                      PurchLine.SETRANGE("Document Type", PurchHeader."Document Type");
                                                                      IF PurchLine.FINDSET THEN
                                                                        REPEAT
                                                                          PurchLine."Responsibility Center" := RespCtr.Code;
                                                                          PurchLine.MODIFY;
                                                                        UNTIL PurchLine.NEXT = 0;
                                                                    UNTIL PurchHeader.NEXT = 0;
                                                                    MESSAGE(Text006, "User ID", PurchHeader.TABLECAPTION);
                                                                  END;
                                                                END;
                                                                // PHP End
                                                              END;

                                                   CaptionML=ENU=Purchase Resp. Ctr. Filter }
    { 5900;   ;Service Resp. Ctr. Filter;Code10   ;TableRelation="Responsibility Center";
                                                   CaptionML=ENU=Service Resp. Ctr. Filter }

    { 50515;  ;Employee No.        ;Code20        ;TableRelation=Employee;
                                                   OnValidate=VAR
                                                                UserSetup@1000 : Record 91;
                                                                Employee@1001 : Record 5200;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                // PHP Start
                                                                IF "Employee No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                                                  UserSetup.SETRANGE("Employee No.","Employee No.");
                                                                  IF NOT UserSetup.ISEMPTY THEN
                                                                    FIELDERROR("Employee No.");
                                                                END;

                                                                IF Employee.GET("Employee No.") THEN
                                                                  "Title/Position" := Employee."Job Title"
                                                                ELSE
                                                                  CLEAR("Title/Position");
                                                                // PHP End
                                                              END;
                                                               }

    { 50521;  ;Resource No.        ;Code20        ;TableRelation=Resource;
                                                   OnValidate=VAR
                                                                UserSetup@1000 : Record 91;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                // PHP Start
                                                                IF "Resource No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                                                  UserSetup.SETRANGE("Resource No.","Resource No.");
                                                                  IF NOT UserSetup.ISEMPTY THEN
                                                                    FIELDERROR("Resource No.");
                                                                  VALIDATE("Register Time", TRUE);
                                                                END;
                                                                // PHP End
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 50522;  ;Base Resource Group ;Code20        ;TableRelation="Resource Group";
                                                   OnValidate=VAR
                                                                Resource@1000 : Record 156;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                // PHP Start
                                                                TESTFIELD("Resource No.");
                                                                IF Resource.GET("Resource No.") AND ("Base Resource Group" <> xRec."Base Resource Group") AND ("Base Resource Group" <> '') THEN BEGIN
                                                                  Resource.VALIDATE("Resource Group No.", "Base Resource Group");
                                                                  Resource.MODIFY;
                                                                END;
                                                                // PHP End
                                                              END;
                                                               }

    Time=[ 2:13:33 PM];

  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    OnInsert=BEGIN
               Default := NoDefaultExists(FALSE);
             END;

    OnDelete=VAR
               NotificationSetup@1000 : Record 1512;
             BEGIN
               IF Default THEN
                 ERROR(DefaultErr);

               NotificationSetup.SETRANGE("Notification Template Code",Code);
               IF NotificationSetup.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                 IF NOT CONFIRM(DeleteTemplateQst) THEN
                   EXIT;
                 NotificationSetup.MODIFYALL("Notification Template Code",'');
               END;
             END;

    CaptionML=ENU=Notification Template;
    LookupPageID=Page1510;
  }

                                                                IF ("Notification Method" <> xRec."Notification Method") AND IsUsed THEN
                                                                  ERROR(STRSUBSTNO(ModifyUsedTemplateErr,FIELDCAPTION("Notification Method")));

    PROCEDURE ExportNotification@5(UseDialog@1002 : Boolean) : Text;
    VAR
      TempBlob@1000 : Record 99008535;
      FileMgt@1001 : Codeunit 419;
      OutStream@1004 : OutStream;
      FileName@1003 : Text;
      NotificationBody@1005 : Text;
      NotificationHeader@1006 : Text;
      NotificationFooter@1007 : Text;
    BEGIN
      NotificationBody := GetNotificationBody;
      NotificationHeader := GetNotificationHeader;
      NotificationFooter := GetNotificationFooter;

      FileName := TABLECAPTION + ' ' + Code;
      CASE "Notification Method" OF
        "Notification Method"::"E-mail":
          FileName += '.htm';
        "Notification Method"::Note:
          FileName += '.txt';
        ELSE
          FileName += '.txt';
      END;
      TempBlob.Blob.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStream);
      OutStream.WRITETEXT(NotificationHeader);
      IF (NotificationHeader <> '') AND (NotificationFooter <> '') THEN
        NotificationBody := IteratorStartTxt + NotificationBody + IteratorEndTxt;
      OutStream.WRITETEXT(NotificationBody);
      OutStream.WRITETEXT(NotificationFooter);

      EXIT(FileMgt.BLOBExport(TempBlob,FileName,UseDialog));
    END;

    PROCEDURE ImportNotification@7();
    VAR
      TempBlob@1001 : Record 99008535;
      FileMgt@1000 : Codeunit 419;
      FileFilter@1002 : Text;
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS("Notification Body");
      IF "Notification Body".HASVALUE THEN
        IF NOT CONFIRM(ReplaceBodyQst,FALSE) THEN
          EXIT;

      CASE "Notification Method" OF
        "Notification Method"::"E-mail":
          FileFilter := FileFilterTxt;
        "Notification Method"::Note:
          FileFilter := FileMgt.GetToFilterText('','*.txt');
        ELSE
          FileFilter := FileFilterTxt;
      END;

      IF FileMgt.BLOBImportWithFilter(TempBlob,ImportTxt,'',FileFilter,FileFilterExtensionTxt) = '' THEN
        EXIT;

      ImportNotificationText(TempBlob.ReadAsText(Environment.NewLine,TEXTENCODING::MSDos));
    END;

    PROCEDURE ImportNotificationText@11(NotificationContent@1004 : Text);
    VAR
      NotificationHeader@1003 : Text;
      NotificationFooter@1002 : Text;
      NotificationBody@1001 : Text;
    BEGIN
      CLEAR("Notification Header");
      CLEAR("Notification Footer");
      CLEAR("Notification Body");

      SplitNotificationIntoParts(NotificationContent,NotificationHeader,NotificationFooter,NotificationBody);
      WriteNotificationHeader(NotificationHeader);
      WriteNotificationFooter(NotificationFooter);
      WriteNotificationBody(NotificationBody);
      MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE DeleteNotification@10();
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS("Notification Body");
      IF "Notification Body".HASVALUE THEN
        IF NOT CONFIRM(DeleteBodyQst,FALSE) THEN
          EXIT;

      CLEAR("Notification Header");
      CLEAR("Notification Footer");
      CLEAR("Notification Body");
      MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetNotificationBody@12() : Text;
    BEGIN
      EXIT(ReadBLOB(FIELDNO("Notification Body")));
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetNotificationHeader@1() : Text;
    BEGIN
      EXIT(ReadBLOB(FIELDNO("Notification Header")));
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetNotificationFooter@2() : Text;
    BEGIN
      EXIT(ReadBLOB(FIELDNO("Notification Footer")));
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ReadBLOB@3(FieldNo@1002 : Integer) : Text;
    VAR
      RecordRef@1001 : RecordRef;
      FieldRef@1003 : FieldRef;
    BEGIN
      RecordRef.GETTABLE(Rec);
      FieldRef := RecordRef.FIELD(FieldNo);
      EXIT(TypeHelper.ReadTextBlob(FieldRef,Environment.NewLine));
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SplitNotificationIntoParts@15(NotificationContent@1000 : Text;VAR NotificationHeader@1001 : Text;VAR NotificationFooter@1002 : Text;VAR NotificationBody@1003 : Text);
    VAR
      IteratorStartPos@1004 : Integer;
      IteratorEndPos@1005 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      IteratorStartPos := STRPOS(NotificationContent,IteratorStartTxt);
      IteratorEndPos := STRPOS(NotificationContent,IteratorEndTxt);
      IF (IteratorStartPos <> 0) AND (IteratorEndPos <> 0) THEN BEGIN
        NotificationHeader := COPYSTR(NotificationContent,1,IteratorStartPos - 1);
        NotificationBody :=
          COPYSTR(
            NotificationContent,IteratorStartPos + STRLEN(IteratorStartTxt),
            IteratorEndPos - (IteratorStartPos + STRLEN(IteratorStartTxt)));
        NotificationFooter := COPYSTR(NotificationContent,IteratorEndPos + STRLEN(IteratorEndTxt));
      END ELSE
        IF (IteratorStartPos = 0) AND (IteratorEndPos = 0) THEN
          NotificationBody := NotificationContent
        ELSE
          ERROR(MissingIteratorIdentifierErr);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE WriteNotificationBody@8(Content@1000 : Text);
    VAR
      OutStream@1001 : OutStream;
    BEGIN
      "Notification Body".CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStream);
      OutStream.WRITETEXT(Content);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE WriteNotificationHeader@6(Content@1000 : Text);
    VAR
      OutStream@1001 : OutStream;
    BEGIN
      "Notification Header".CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStream);
      OutStream.WRITETEXT(Content);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE WriteNotificationFooter@16(Content@1000 : Text);
    VAR
      OutStream@1001 : OutStream;
    BEGIN
      "Notification Footer".CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStream);
      OutStream.WRITETEXT(Content);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE NoDefaultExists@4(ClearDefaults@1001 : Boolean) : Boolean;
    VAR
      NotificationTemplate@1000 : Record 1510;
    BEGIN
      NotificationTemplate.SETFILTER(Code,'<>%1',Code);
      NotificationTemplate.SETRANGE(Type,Type);
      NotificationTemplate.SETRANGE(Default,TRUE);
      IF ClearDefaults THEN
        NotificationTemplate.MODIFYALL(Default,FALSE);
      EXIT(NotificationTemplate.ISEMPTY);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE IsUsed@13() : Boolean;
    VAR
      NotificationSetup@1000 : Record 1512;
    BEGIN
      NotificationSetup.SETRANGE("Notification Template Code",Code);
      EXIT(NotificationSetup.FINDFIRST);
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

    PROCEDURE CreateNew@1(NewType@1003 : Option;NewUserID@1002 : Code[50];NewRecord@1000 : Variant;NewLinkTargetPage@1004 : Integer;NewCustomLink@1005 : Text[250]);
    VAR
      NewRecRef@1001 : RecordRef;
      NotifTemplate@1006 : Record 1510;
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start - NOT-01
      // Added Approval-RFE in NewType local variable
      // Remove the Option value in NewType Local variable.
      // PHP End
      IF NOT DataTypeManagement.GetRecordRef(NewRecord,NewRecRef) THEN
        EXIT;
      CLEAR(Rec);
      Type := NewType;
      "Recipient User ID" := NewUserID;
      "Triggered By Record" := NewRecRef.RECORDID;
      "Link Target Page" := NewLinkTargetPage;
      "Custom Link" := NewCustomLink;

      INSERT(TRUE);
    END;

    PROCEDURE CreateNew2@2(NewType@1003 : Option;NewUserID@1002 : Code[50];NewRecord@1000 : Variant;NewLinkTargetPage@1004 : Integer;NewCustomLink@1005 : Text[250];CcTxt@1007 : Text[250];FilePath@1008 : Text[250];FileName@1009 : Text[250];NewSubject@1000000000 : Text[250]);
    VAR
      NewRecRef@1001 : RecordRef;
      NotifTemplate@1006 : Record 1510;
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start - With cc copy features
      IF NOT DataTypeManagement.GetRecordRef(NewRecord,NewRecRef) THEN
        EXIT;
      CLEAR(Rec);
      Type := NewType;
      "Recipient User ID" := NewUserID;
      "Triggered By Record" := NewRecRef.RECORDID;
      "Link Target Page" := NewLinkTargetPage;
      "Custom Link" := NewCustomLink;
      "Send CC" := CcTxt;
      "Attachment File Path" := FilePath;
      "Attachment Name" := FileName;
      "Email Subject" := NewSubject;
      INSERT(TRUE);
      // PHP End
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }

OBJECT Table 1512 Notification Setup
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=06/26/18;
    Time=[ 2:43:43 AM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=NAVW19.00,NOT-01,NAVOC1.00.02,ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    OnInsert=BEGIN
               TESTFIELD("Notification Template Code");
             END;

    OnDelete=VAR
               NotificationSchedule@1000 : Record 1513;
             BEGIN

                                                                NotificationTemplate@1000 : Record 1510;
                                                              BEGIN

                                                                  NotificationTemplate."Notification Method"::Note:
                                                                    "Non-Aggregated Notifications" := TRUE;
                                                                END;
                                                              END;

    { 4   ;   ;Non-Aggregated Notifications;Boolean;
                                                   OnValidate=VAR
                                                                NotificationTemplate@1000 : Record 1510;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                IF (NOT "Non-Aggregated Notifications") AND NotificationTemplate.GET("Notification Template Code") THEN
                                                                  CASE NotificationTemplate."Notification Method" OF
                                                                    NotificationTemplate."Notification Method"::Note:
                                                                      ERROR(IndividualNotificationMustBeActiveErr,FIELDCAPTION("Non-Aggregated Notifications"),
                                                                        NotificationTemplate.TABLECAPTION,FORMAT(NotificationTemplate."Notification Method"));
                                                                  END;
                                                              END;

                                                   CaptionML=ENU=Non-Aggregated Notifications }
    { 5   ;   ;Schedule            ;Option        ;FieldClass=FlowField;
                                                   CalcFormula=Lookup("Notification Schedule".Recurrence WHERE (User ID=FIELD(User ID),
                                                                                                                Notification Type=FIELD(Notification Type)));
                                                   CaptionML=ENU=Schedule;
                                                   OptionCaptionML=ENU=Instantly,Daily,Weekly,Monthly;
                                                   OptionString=Instantly,Daily,Weekly,Monthly }
  }
  KEYS
  {
    {    ;User ID,Notification Type               ;Clustered=Yes }
  }
  FIELDGROUPS
  {
  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      IndividualNotificationMustBeActiveErr@1001 : TextConst '@@@="%1 is caption of field ""Non-Aggregated Notifications"", %2 is caption of table ""Notification Template"", %3 = the option value in ""Notification Template"".""Notification Method"" ex. ""Note""";ENU=%1 must be active when the %2 is of type %3.';

    BEGIN
    END.
  }

  }
  CODE
  {

    PROCEDURE NewRecord@4(NewUserID@1000 : Code[50];NewNotificationType@1001 : Option);
    BEGIN
      INIT;
      "User ID" := NewUserID;
      "Notification Type" := NewNotificationType;

      INSERT;
    END;

    PROCEDURE ScheduledAt@3(DateTime@1000 : DateTime;LastUpdateDateTime@1002 : DateTime) : Boolean;
    VAR
      Date@1001 : Date;
    BEGIN
      Date := DT2DATE(DateTime);

      CASE Recurrence OF
        Recurrence::Instantly:
          EXIT(TRUE);
        Recurrence::Daily,
        Recurrence::Weekly:
          IF NotifyWeekday(Date) THEN
            IF (LastUpdateDateTime < CREATEDATETIME(Date,Time)) AND (DateTime >= CREATEDATETIME(Date,Time)) THEN
              EXIT(TRUE);
        Recurrence::Monthly:
          CASE "Monthly Notification Date" OF
            "Monthly Notification Date"::"First Workday":
              IF GetFirstWorkdateOfMonth(Date) = Date THEN
                IF (LastUpdateDateTime < CREATEDATETIME(Date,Time)) AND (DateTime >= CREATEDATETIME(Date,Time)) THEN
                  EXIT(TRUE);
            "Monthly Notification Date"::"Last Workday":
              IF GetLastWorkdateOfMonth(Date) = Date THEN
                IF (LastUpdateDateTime < CREATEDATETIME(Date,Time)) AND (DateTime >= CREATEDATETIME(Date,Time)) THEN
                  EXIT(TRUE);
            "Monthly Notification Date"::Custom:
              IF DATE2DMY(TODAY,1) = "Date of Month" THEN
                IF (LastUpdateDateTime < CREATEDATETIME(Date,Time)) AND (DateTime >= CREATEDATETIME(Date,Time)) THEN
                  EXIT(TRUE);
          END;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE NotifyWeekday@1(Date@1001 : Date) : Boolean;
    VAR
      Day@1000 : ',Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday,Sunday';
    BEGIN
      CASE DATE2DWY(Date,1) OF
        Day::Monday:
          EXIT(Monday);
        Day::Tuesday:
          EXIT(Tuesday);
        Day::Wednesday:
          EXIT(Wednesday);
        Day::Thursday:
          EXIT(Thursday);
        Day::Friday:
          EXIT(Friday);
        Day::Saturday:
          EXIT(Saturday);
        Day::Sunday:
          EXIT(Sunday);
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE UpdateDailyFrequency@8();
    BEGIN
      Monday := TRUE;
      Tuesday := TRUE;
      Wednesday := TRUE;
      Thursday := TRUE;
      Friday := TRUE;
      Saturday := "Daily Frequency" <> "Daily Frequency"::Weekday;
      Sunday := "Daily Frequency" <> "Daily Frequency"::Weekday;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetFirstWorkdateOfMonth@2(CurrentDate@1000 : Date) : Date;
    VAR
      Day@1002 : ',Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday,Sunday';
    BEGIN
      IF DATE2DWY(CALCDATE('<-CM>',CurrentDate),1) IN [Day::Saturday,Day::Sunday] THEN
        EXIT(CALCDATE('<-CM+WD1>',CurrentDate));

      EXIT(CALCDATE('<-CM>',CurrentDate))
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetLastWorkdateOfMonth@5(CurrentDate@1000 : Date) : Date;
    VAR
      Day@1002 : ',Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday,Sunday';
    BEGIN
      IF DATE2DWY(CALCDATE('<+CM>',CurrentDate),1) IN [Day::Saturday,Day::Sunday] THEN
        EXIT(CALCDATE('<+CM-WD5>',CurrentDate));

      EXIT(CALCDATE('<+CM>',CurrentDate))
    END;

    BEGIN
    {
      PHP Start - NOT-01
      Added Approval-RFE in NewType local varial
      PHP End
    }
    END.
  }
}

  CODE
  {

    PROCEDURE NewRecord@11(NotificationEntry@1000 : Record 1511;NotificationContent@1001 : Text;NotificationMethod@1005 : Option);
    VAR
      OutStream@1004 : OutStream;
    BEGIN
      CLEAR(Rec);
      TRANSFERFIELDS(NotificationEntry);
      "Notification Content".CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStream);
      OutStream.WRITETEXT(NotificationContent);
      "Notification Method" := NotificationMethod;
      "Sent Date-Time" := CURRENTDATETIME;
      INSERT(TRUE);
    END;

    PROCEDURE ExportContent@2(UseDialog@1002 : Boolean) : Text;
    VAR
      TempBlob@1000 : Record 99008535;
      FileMgt@1001 : Codeunit 419;
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS("Notification Content");
      IF "Notification Content".HASVALUE THEN BEGIN
        TempBlob.Blob := "Notification Content";
        IF "Notification Method" = "Notification Method"::Note THEN
          EXIT(FileMgt.BLOBExport(TempBlob,'*.txt',UseDialog));
        EXIT(FileMgt.BLOBExport(TempBlob,'*.htm',UseDialog))
      END;
    END;

    BEGIN
    {
      PHP Start - NOT-01
      Added Approval-RFE in NewType local varial
      PHP End
    }
    END.
  }
}

OBJECT Table 5200 Employee
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=06/26/18;
    Time=[ 3:39:47 PM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=NAVW19.00.00.49968,ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    DataCaptionFields=No.,First Name,Middle Name,Last Name;
    OnInsert=BEGIN
               IF "No." = '' THEN BEGIN
                 HumanResSetup.GET;
                 HumanResSetup.TESTFIELD("Employee Nos.");
                 NoSeriesMgt.InitSeries(HumanResSetup."Employee Nos.",xRec."No. Series",0D,"No.","No. Series");
               END;

               DimMgt.UpdateDefaultDim(
                 DATABASE::Employee,"No.",
                 "Global Dimension 1 Code","Global Dimension 2 Code");
               // PHP Start
               "Created At" := TODAY;
               // PHP End
             END;

    OnModify=BEGIN
               "Last Date Modified" := TODAY;
                IF Res.READPERMISSION THEN
                 EmployeeResUpdate.HumanResToRes(xRec,Rec);
                IF SalespersonPurchaser.READPERMISSION THEN
                 EmployeeSalespersonUpdate.HumanResToSalesPerson(xRec,Rec);
             END;

    OnDelete=BEGIN
               AlternativeAddr.SETRANGE("Employee No.","No.");
               AlternativeAddr.DELETEALL;

               EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE("Employee No.","No.");
               EmployeeQualification.DELETEALL;

               Relative.SETRANGE("Employee No.","No.");
               Relative.DELETEALL;

               EmployeeAbsence.SETRANGE("Employee No.","No.");
               EmployeeAbsence.DELETEALL;

               MiscArticleInformation.SETRANGE("Employee No.","No.");
               MiscArticleInformation.DELETEALL;

               ConfidentialInformation.SETRANGE("Employee No.","No.");
               ConfidentialInformation.DELETEALL;

               HumanResComment.SETRANGE("No.","No.");
               HumanResComment.DELETEALL;

               DimMgt.DeleteDefaultDim(DATABASE::Employee,"No.");


               // PHP Start - for Maritime
               EmployeeCharacterReference.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
               EmployeeCharacterReference.DELETEALL;

               EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
               EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.DELETEALL;

               ApprovalsMgmt.DeleteApprovalEntries(RECORDID);
               // PHP End
             END;

    OnRename=BEGIN
               "Last Date Modified" := TODAY;
             END;

    CaptionML=ENU=Employee;
    LookupPageID=Page5201;
    DrillDownPageID=Page5201;

                                                                END;

    { 500001; ;Approver Code       ;Code20        ;TableRelation=Employee;
                                                   OnValidate=VAR
                                                                UserSetup@1000 : Record 91;
                                                                ApproverUserID@1001 : Code[50];
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                // PHP Start
                                                                IF UserSetup.WRITEPERMISSION THEN BEGIN
                                                                  UserSetup.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "Approver Code");
                                                                  IF NOT UserSetup.FINDFIRST THEN
                                                                    EXIT;
                                                                  ApproverUserID := UserSetup."User ID";
                                                                  UserSetup.RESET;
                                                                  IF UserSetup.GET("User ID") THEN BEGIN
                                                                    UserSetup.VALIDATE("Approver ID", ApproverUserID);
                                                                    IF UserSetup.MODIFY(TRUE) THEN
                                                                      MESSAGE(Text001, UserSetup.FIELDCAPTION("Approver ID"), "User ID", ApproverUserID, UserSetup.TABLECAPTION);
                                                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                                                    UserSetup.RESET;
                                                                    UserSetup.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
                                                                    IF NOT UserSetup.FINDFIRST THEN
                                                                      EXIT;
                                                                    UserSetup.VALIDATE("Approver ID", ApproverUserID);
                                                                    "User ID" := UserSetup."User ID";
                                                                    IF UserSetup.MODIFY(TRUE) THEN
                                                                      MESSAGE(Text001, UserSetup.FIELDCAPTION("Approver ID"), "User ID", ApproverUserID, UserSetup.TABLECAPTION);
                                                                  END;
                                                                END;
                                                                // PHP End
                                                              END;
                                                               }

    { 500454; ;Middle Initial      ;Text3         ;OnValidate=VAR
                                                                StringPos@1000 : Integer;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                // PHP Start
                                                                "Middle Initial" := DELCHR("Middle Initial", '=', ' .');
                                                                IF "Middle Initial" <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                                                  StringPos := STRPOS("Middle Initial", '.') - 1;
                                                                  IF StringPos < 1 THEN
                                                                    "Middle Initial" := UPPERCASE("Middle Initial" + '.')
                                                                  ELSE
                                                                    "Middle Initial" := UPPERCASE("Middle Initial");
                                                                END;
                                                                "Search Name" := FormalName;

                                                                // PHP End
                                                              END;
                                                               }

      ApprovalsMgmt@1000000003 : Codeunit 1535;
      NoSeriesMgt@1012 : Codeunit 396;
      EmployeeResUpdate@1013 : Codeunit 5200;
      EmployeeSalespersonUpdate@1014 : Codeunit 5201;
      DimMgt@1015 : Codeunit 408;
      Text000@1016 : TextConst 'ENU=Before you can use Online Map, you must fill in the Online Map Setup window.\See Setting Up Online Map in Help.';
      Text001@1017 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 of %2 has been successfully updated to %3 in %4.';

    PROCEDURE AssistEdit@2(OldEmployee@1000 : Record 5200) : Boolean;
    BEGIN
      WITH Employee DO BEGIN
        Employee := Rec;
        HumanResSetup.GET;
        HumanResSetup.TESTFIELD("Employee Nos.");
        IF NoSeriesMgt.SelectSeries(HumanResSetup."Employee Nos.",OldEmployee."No. Series","No. Series") THEN BEGIN
          HumanResSetup.GET;
          HumanResSetup.TESTFIELD("Employee Nos.");
          NoSeriesMgt.SetSeries("No.");
          Rec := Employee;
          EXIT(TRUE);
        END;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE FullName@1() : Text[100];
    BEGIN
      // IF "Middle Name" = '' THEN // PHP Original Code
      IF "Middle Initial" = '' THEN // PHP Start of Modified Code
        EXIT("First Name" + ' ' + "Last Name");
      EXIT("First Name" + ' ' + "Middle Initial" + ' ' + "Last Name"); // PHP Start of Modified Code
      // EXIT("First Name" + ' ' + "Middle Name" + ' ' + "Last Name"); // PHP Original Code
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ValidateShortcutDimCode@29(FieldNumber@1000 : Integer;VAR ShortcutDimCode@1001 : Code[20]);
    BEGIN
      DimMgt.ValidateDimValueCode(FieldNumber,ShortcutDimCode);
      DimMgt.SaveDefaultDim(DATABASE::Employee,"No.",FieldNumber,ShortcutDimCode);
      MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE DisplayMap@7();
    VAR
      MapPoint@1001 : Record 800;
      MapMgt@1000 : Codeunit 802;
    BEGIN
      IF MapPoint.FINDFIRST THEN
        MapMgt.MakeSelection(DATABASE::Employee,GETPOSITION)
      ELSE
        MESSAGE(Text000);
    END;

    PROCEDURE FormalName@8() : Text;
    VAR
      FName@1000 : Text;
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      IF ("Last Name" <> '') AND ("First Name" = '') THEN
        FName := "Last Name" + '';
      IF ("Last Name" = '') AND ("First Name" <> '') THEN
        FName := "First Name" + '';
      IF ("Last Name" <> '') AND ("First Name" <> '') AND ("Middle Initial" = '') THEN
        FName := "Last Name" + ', ' + "First Name";
      IF ("Last Name" <> '') AND ("First Name" <> '') THEN
        FName := "Last Name" + ', ' + "First Name" + ' ' + "Middle Initial";

      EXIT(UPPERCASE(FName));
      // PHP End
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetMiddleInitial@16();
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      IF "Middle Name" <> '' THEN BEGIN

      "Middle Initial" := UPPERCASE(COPYSTR("Middle Name",1,1)) + '.';
      END;
      // PHP End
    END;

    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetAge@1000000004() : Integer;
    VAR
      TempAge@1000000000 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      TempAge := 0;
      IF "Birth Date" = 0D THEN
        EXIT(TempAge);

      TempAge := DATE2DMY(TODAY, 3) - DATE2DMY("Birth Date", 3);
      IF TempAge <= 0 THEN
        EXIT(0);

      IF CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1Y>',TempAge),"Birth Date") > TODAY THEN
          TempAge -= 1;

      EXIT(TempAge);
      // PHP End
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetPicture@1000000006(PictureTxt@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      OutStr@1000000004 : OutStream;
      Bytes@1000000003 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      IF PictureTxt = '' THEN BEGIN
        CALCFIELDS(Picture);
        CLEAR(Picture);
        MODIFY;
        EXIT;
      END;

      Bytes := Convert.FromBase64String(PictureTxt);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream(Bytes);
      Picture.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      MemoryStream.WriteTo(OutStr);

      MODIFY;
      // PHP End
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetPicture@1000000007(VAR PictureTxt@1000000004 : Text);
    VAR
      InStr@1000000003 : InStream;
      Bytes@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS(Picture);
      IF NOT Picture.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT;

      Picture.CREATEINSTREAM(InStr);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream();
      COPYSTREAM(MemoryStream, InStr);
      Bytes := MemoryStream.GetBuffer();
      PictureTxt := Convert.ToBase64String(Bytes);
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetAdditionalProvision@1000000002(NewBigTxt@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      OutStr@1000000001 : OutStream;
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS("Additional Provision");
      IF (NOT "Additional Provision".HASVALUE) AND (NewBigTxt = '') THEN
        EXIT;

      IF NewBigTxt = '' THEN BEGIN
        CLEAR("Additional Provision");
        MODIFY;
        EXIT;
      END;

      "Additional Provision".CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      OutStr.WRITETEXT(NewBigTxt);
      IF "No." <> '' THEN
        MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetAdditionalProvision@1000000000() : Text;
    VAR
      NewBigTxt@1000000000 : Text;
      InStr@1000000001 : InStream;
    BEGIN
      NewBigTxt := '';
      CALCFIELDS("Additional Provision");
      IF NOT "Additional Provision".HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT('');

      "Additional Provision".CREATEINSTREAM(InStr);
      InStr.READTEXT(NewBigTxt);

      EXIT(NewBigTxt);
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetQualificationPerPosition@1000000003();
    VAR
      EmpQualification@1000000001 : Record 5203;
      EmployeeQualification2@1000000002 : Record 5203;
      DefaultQualificationValues@1000000000 : Record 59031;
      LineNo@1000000003 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      // Set the applicant qualification based on the Position
      IF ("Current Rank Code" <> '') AND ("Current Rank Code" <> xRec."Current Rank Code") THEN BEGIN
        // Set the Line No.
        EmployeeQualification2.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
        LineNo := EmployeeQualification2.GetLastNo;

        DefaultQualificationValues.SETRANGE("Table ID", DATABASE::Position);
        DefaultQualificationValues.SETRANGE("No.", "Current Rank Code");
        IF DefaultQualificationValues.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
          REPEAT
            EmpQualification.RESET;
            EmpQualification.SETCURRENTKEY("Employee No.", "Qualification Code", Archived);
            EmpQualification.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
            EmpQualification.SETRANGE("Qualification Code", DefaultQualificationValues."Qualification Code");
            EmpQualification.SETRANGE(Archived, FALSE);
            IF NOT EmpQualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
              EmpQualification."Employee No." := "No.";
              EmployeeQualification."Line No." := LineNo + 10000;
              EmpQualification.VALIDATE("Qualification Code", DefaultQualificationValues."Qualification Code");
              EmpQualification.INSERT;
            END;
            CLEAR(EmpQualification);
          UNTIL DefaultQualificationValues.NEXT = 0;
        END;
      END;
      // PHP End
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GenerateOfferLetter@1000000012();
    VAR
      Employee@1000000004 : Record 5200;
      EmployeeQualification@1000000006 : Record 5203;
      NewEmployeeQualification@1000000010 : Record 5203;
      EmployeeQualificationLastNo@1000000011 : Record 5203;
      Qualification@1000000005 : Record 5202;
      TempBlob@1000000003 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      LineNo@1000000008 : Integer;
      FileManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 419;
      FilePath@1000000000 : Text;
      ErrOfferLetterQualification@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=Please setup the Offer Letter as qualification in the Qualification List or contact your administrator.';
      ErrServerFilePath@1000000007 : TextConst 'ENU=Server file path for the report %1 not found. Please contact your administrator.';
      ErrNoQualificaitonSetup@1000000009 : TextConst 'ENU=Please setup a Qualification for the Type ''%1'' or contact your administrator.';
    BEGIN
       // Generate Offer Letter
       IF "On-Boarding Process" <> xRec."On-Boarding Process" THEN
         MODIFY;

       Employee.SETRANGE("No.", "No.");
       FilePath := FileManagement.ServerTempFileName('pdf');
       REPORT.SAVEASPDF(REPORT::"Employee Offer Letter", FilePath, Employee);
       IF FileManagement.ServerFileExists(FilePath) THEN BEGIN
        TempBlob.INIT;
        FileManagement.BLOBImportFromServerFile(TempBlob,FilePath);
        TempBlob.INSERT;
        TempBlob.CALCFIELDS(Blob);

        Qualification.SETRANGE(Type, Qualification.Type::"Offer Letter");
        IF Qualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          // Get the last no of Employee Qualification
          EmployeeQualificationLastNo.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
          LineNo := EmployeeQualificationLastNo.GetLastNo + 10000;

          // Start of Insert and modify of Employee Qualification
          EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
          EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE("Qualification Code", Qualification.Code);
          EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE(Archived, FALSE);
          IF EmployeeQualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
            EmployeeQualification.ArchiveEmployeeQualification;
            EmployeeQualification.CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      //      CLEAR(EmployeeQualification.Attachment);
            EmployeeQualification.Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
            EmployeeQualification."Offer Letter Accepted" := FALSE;
            EmployeeQualification.MODIFY;
          END ELSE BEGIN
            NewEmployeeQualification.INIT;
            NewEmployeeQualification."Employee No." := "No.";
            NewEmployeeQualification."Line No." := LineNo;
            NewEmployeeQualification.VALIDATE("Qualification Code", Qualification.Code);
      //      NewEmployeeQualification."From Date" := "Start Date";
      //      NewEmployeeQualification."To Date" := "End Date";
            NewEmployeeQualification."Document No." := FORMAT(Rec.RECORDID);
      //      NewEmployeeQualification."Expiration Date" := "Expiry Date";
            NewEmployeeQualification.Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
            NewEmployeeQualification.VALIDATE("File Extension", 'pdf');
            NewEmployeeQualification."Has Attachment" := TRUE;
            NewEmployeeQualification.INSERT;
          END;
        END ELSE
          ERROR(ErrNoQualificaitonSetup, Qualification.Type::"Offer Letter");
       END ELSE
        ERROR(ErrServerFilePath, Qualification.Type::"Offer Letter");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GenerateContract@1000000001();
    VAR
      Employee@1000000004 : Record 5200;
      EmployeeQualification@1000000006 : Record 5203;
      NewEmployeeQualification@1000000010 : Record 5203;
      EmployeeQualificationLastNo@1000000011 : Record 5203;
      Qualification@1000000005 : Record 5202;
      TempBlob@1000000003 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      LineNo@1000000008 : Integer;
      FileManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 419;
      FilePath@1000000000 : Text;
      ErrOfferLetterQualification@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=Please setup the Offer Letter as qualification in the Qualification List or contact your administrator.';
      ErrServerFilePath@1000000007 : TextConst 'ENU=Server file path for the report %1 not found. Please contact your administrator.';
      ErrNoQualificaitonSetup@1000000009 : TextConst 'ENU=Please setup a Qualification for the Type ''%1'' or contact your administrator.';
    BEGIN
       // Generate Contract
       IF "On-Boarding Process" <> xRec."On-Boarding Process" THEN
         MODIFY;

       Employee.SETRANGE("No.", "No.");
       FilePath := FileManagement.ServerTempFileName('pdf');
       REPORT.SAVEASPDF(REPORT::"Employee Contract", FilePath, Employee);
       IF FileManagement.ServerFileExists(FilePath) THEN BEGIN
        TempBlob.INIT;
        FileManagement.BLOBImportFromServerFile(TempBlob,FilePath);
        TempBlob.INSERT;
        TempBlob.CALCFIELDS(Blob);

        Qualification.SETRANGE(Type, Qualification.Type::Contract);
        IF Qualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          // Get the last no of Employee Qualification
          EmployeeQualificationLastNo.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
          LineNo := EmployeeQualificationLastNo.GetLastNo + 10000;

          // Start of Insert and modify of Employee Qualification
          EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
          EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE("Qualification Code", Qualification.Code);
          EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE(Archived, FALSE);
          IF EmployeeQualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
            EmployeeQualification.ArchiveEmployeeQualification;
            EmployeeQualification.CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
            CLEAR(EmployeeQualification.Attachment);
            EmployeeQualification.Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
            EmployeeQualification."Contract Accepted" := FALSE;
            EmployeeQualification.MODIFY;
          END ELSE BEGIN
            NewEmployeeQualification.INIT;
            NewEmployeeQualification."Employee No." := "No.";
            NewEmployeeQualification."Line No." := LineNo;
            NewEmployeeQualification.VALIDATE("Qualification Code", Qualification.Code);
      //      NewEmployeeQualification."From Date" := "Start Date";
      //      NewEmployeeQualification."To Date" := "End Date";
            NewEmployeeQualification."Document No." := FORMAT(Rec.RECORDID);
      //      NewEmployeeQualification."Expiration Date" := "Expiry Date";
            NewEmployeeQualification.Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
            NewEmployeeQualification.VALIDATE("File Extension", 'pdf');
            NewEmployeeQualification."Has Attachment" := TRUE;
            NewEmployeeQualification.INSERT;
          END;
        END ELSE
          ERROR(ErrNoQualificaitonSetup, Qualification.Type::Contract);
       END ELSE
        ERROR(ErrServerFilePath, Qualification.Type::Contract);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GeneratePlaneTicketQualification@1000000026();
    VAR
      EmployeeQualificationLastNo@1000000003 : Record 5203;
      NewEmployeeQualification@1000000001 : Record 5203;
      Qualification@1000000000 : Record 5202;
      LineNo@1000000002 : Integer;
      ErrNoQualificaitonSetup@1000000004 : TextConst 'ENU=Please setup a Qualification for the Type ''%1'' or contact your administrator.';
    BEGIN
      Qualification.SETRANGE(Type, Qualification.Type::"Travel Ticket");
      IF Qualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
        EmployeeQualificationLastNo.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
        LineNo := EmployeeQualificationLastNo.GetLastNo + 10000;

        EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
        EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE("Qualification Code", Qualification.Code);
        EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE(Archived, FALSE);
        IF EmployeeQualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          EmployeeQualification.ArchiveEmployeeQualification;
          EmployeeQualification.MODIFY;
        END ELSE BEGIN
          NewEmployeeQualification.INIT;
            NewEmployeeQualification."Employee No." := "No.";
            NewEmployeeQualification."Line No." := LineNo;
            NewEmployeeQualification.VALIDATE("Qualification Code", Qualification.Code);
            NewEmployeeQualification."Document No." := FORMAT(Rec.RECORDID);
            NewEmployeeQualification.INSERT;
        END;
      END ELSE
        ERROR(ErrNoQualificaitonSetup, Qualification.Type::"Travel Ticket");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GenerateGuaranteeLetter@1000000028();
    VAR
      Employee@1000000005 : Record 5200;
      EmployeeQualification@1000000010 : Record 5203;
      NewEmployeeQualification@1000000001 : Record 5203;
      EmployeeQualificationLastNo@1000000008 : Record 5203;
      Qualification@1000000000 : Record 5202;
      ErrNoPlaneTicketQualification@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=Please setup a Qualification for the Type ''Travel Ticket'' or contact your administrator.';
      JobApplication@1000000007 : Record 59025;
      TempBlob@1000000006 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      FileManagement@1000000004 : Codeunit 419;
      FilePath@1000000003 : Text;
      LineNo@1000000009 : Integer;
      ErrServerFilePath@1000000012 : TextConst 'ENU=Server file path for the report %1 not found. Please contact your administrator.';
      ErrNoQualificaitonSetup@1000000011 : TextConst 'ENU=Please setup a Qualification for the Type ''%1'' or contact your administrator.';
    BEGIN
       IF "On-Boarding Process" <> xRec."On-Boarding Process" THEN
        MODIFY;

       Employee.SETRANGE("No.", "No.");
       FilePath := FileManagement.ServerTempFileName('pdf');
       REPORT.SAVEASPDF(REPORT::"Employee Guarantee Letter", FilePath, Employee);
       IF FileManagement.ServerFileExists(FilePath) THEN BEGIN
        TempBlob.INIT;
        FileManagement.BLOBImportFromServerFile(TempBlob,FilePath);
        TempBlob.INSERT;
        TempBlob.CALCFIELDS(Blob);

        Qualification.SETRANGE(Type,Qualification.Type::"Letter of Guarantee");
        IF  Qualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          EmployeeQualificationLastNo.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
          LineNo := EmployeeQualificationLastNo.GetLastNo + 10000;

          EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
          EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE("Qualification Code", Qualification.Code);
          EmployeeQualification.SETRANGE(Archived, FALSE);
          IF EmployeeQualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
            EmployeeQualification.ArchiveEmployeeQualification;
            EmployeeQualification.CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
            CLEAR(EmployeeQualification.Attachment);
            EmployeeQualification.Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
            EmployeeQualification.MODIFY;
          END ELSE BEGIN
            NewEmployeeQualification.INIT;
            NewEmployeeQualification."Employee No." := "No.";
            NewEmployeeQualification."Line No." := LineNo;
            NewEmployeeQualification.VALIDATE("Qualification Code", Qualification.Code);
            NewEmployeeQualification."Document No." := FORMAT(Rec.RECORDID);
            NewEmployeeQualification.Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
            NewEmployeeQualification.VALIDATE("File Extension", 'pdf');
            NewEmployeeQualification."Has Attachment" := TRUE;
            NewEmployeeQualification.INSERT;
          END;
        END ELSE
          ERROR(ErrNoQualificaitonSetup, Qualification.Type::"Letter of Guarantee");
       END ELSE
        ERROR(ErrServerFilePath, Qualification.Type::"Letter of Guarantee");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetOnBoardingStatus@1000000008(OnBoardingStatus@1000000000 : Integer);
    VAR
      RecordRestrictionMgt@1000000001 : Codeunit 1550;
    BEGIN
      CASE OnBoardingStatus OF
        "On-Boarding Process"::"Offer Extended":
          BEGIN
            RecordRestrictionMgt.CheckRecordHasUsageRestrictions(RECORDID);
            CheckApprovalStatus;
            GenerateOfferLetter;
            ClearOfferDetails;
          END;
        "On-Boarding Process"::"Offer Accepted":
          BEGIN
            "Offer Accepted" := TRUE;
            "Date Offer Accepted" := TODAY;
            GenerateOfferLetter;
            // PHP Start
            GeneratePlaneTicketQualification;
            GenerateVisaQualification;
            GeneratePPE;
            // PHP End
          END;
        "On-Boarding Process"::"Contract Extended":
          BEGIN
            RecordRestrictionMgt.CheckRecordHasUsageRestrictions(RECORDID);
      //      CheckRequiredInfo(OnBoardingStatus);
            GenerateContract;
          END;
        "On-Boarding Process"::"Contract Accepted":
          BEGIN
            RecordRestrictionMgt.CheckRecordHasUsageRestrictions(RECORDID);
            GenerateGuaranteeLetter;
          END;
      //  "On-Boarding Process"::"Offer Accepted":
      //    BEGIN
      //      RecordRestrictionMgt.CheckRecordHasUsageRestrictions(RECORDID);
      //      GeneratePlaneTicketQualification;
      //      GenerateVisaQualification;
      //    END;
        "On-Boarding Process"::"Sign-On":
          BEGIN
            RecordRestrictionMgt.CheckRecordHasUsageRestrictions(RECORDID);
            //GeneratePPE;
            CheckRequiredCrewDetails(OnBoardingStatus);
          END;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ClearOfferDetails@1000000011();
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      CLEAR("Offer Accepted");
      CLEAR("Date Offer Accepted");
      // PHP End
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE CheckApprovalStatus@1000000031();
    VAR
      ApprovalEntry@1000000000 : Record 454;
      Err01@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=The required documents must undergo the approval process.';
    BEGIN
      ApprovalEntry.SETCURRENTKEY("Record ID to Approve", "Last Date-Time Modified");
      ApprovalEntry.SETRANGE("Record ID to Approve", RECORDID);
      ApprovalEntry.SETASCENDING("Last Date-Time Modified", TRUE);
      IF (NOT ApprovalEntry.FINDLAST) OR (ApprovalEntry.Status <> ApprovalEntry.Status::Approved) THEN
        ERROR(Err01);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE CheckRequiredCrewDetails@1000000010(OnBoardingStatus@1000000000 : Integer);
    VAR
      EmpQualification@1000000001 : Record 5203;
      EmpCharacterReference@1000000002 : Record 59035;
      Err01@1000000004 : TextConst 'ENU=Please indicate at least one (1) Character Reference.';
      Err02@1000000003 : TextConst 'ENU=Please indicate at least one (1) Experience.';
      EmpSeaServiceRecord@1000000005 : Record 59034;
    BEGIN
      CASE OnBoardingStatus OF
        "On-Boarding Process"::"Contract Extended":
          BEGIN
            TESTFIELD("Sign-On Date");
            TESTFIELD("Sign-Off Date");
            TESTFIELD("Date of Departure");
            TESTFIELD("Date of Arrival");
            TESTFIELD("Departure Details 1");
            TESTFIELD("Departure Details 2");
            TESTFIELD("Departure Details 3");
            TESTFIELD("Arrival Details 1");
            TESTFIELD("Arrival Details 2");
            TESTFIELD("Arrival Details 3");
          END;
        "On-Boarding Process"::"Sign-On":
          BEGIN
            TESTFIELD("Current Rank Code");
            TESTFIELD("First Name");
            TESTFIELD("Birth Date");
            TESTFIELD(Gender);
            TESTFIELD("HR-Question 1");
            TESTFIELD("Country/Region Code");
            TESTFIELD("E-Mail");
            TESTFIELD("HR-Question 2");
            TESTFIELD(Address);
            TESTFIELD("Religion Code");
            TESTFIELD("Next of Kin Name");
            TESTFIELD("Next of Kin Relationship");
            TESTFIELD("Next of Kin Contact No.");
            TESTFIELD("Date Graduated");
            TESTFIELD(University);
            TESTFIELD("Course/Degree");

            // Check Qualification
            TestEmpQualification;

            // Check character reference
            EmpCharacterReference.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
            IF NOT  EmpCharacterReference.FINDFIRST THEN
              ERROR(Err01);

            // Check sea service record
            EmpSeaServiceRecord.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
            IF NOT EmpSeaServiceRecord.FINDFIRST THEN
              ERROR(Err02);

          END;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestEmpQualification@1000000018();
    VAR
      EmpQualification@1000000000 : Record 5203;
      Qualification@1000000001 : Record 5202;
    BEGIN
      EmpQualification.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "No.");
      EmpQualification.SETRANGE(Archived, FALSE);
      IF EmpQualification.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          Qualification.GET(EmpQualification."Qualification Code");
          IF FORMAT(Qualification."Calculate Expiry") <> '' THEN BEGIN
            EmpQualification.TESTFIELD("From Date");
            EmpQualification.TESTFIELD("To Date");
            EmpQualification.TESTFIELD("Document No.");
          END;
          EmpQualification.CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
          IF NOT EmpQualification.Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
            EmpQualification.TESTFIELD(Attachment);
        UNTIL EmpQualification.NEXT = 0;
      END;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

    PROCEDURE SetAttachment@1000000006(Base64TextToBlob@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      RecRef@1000000006 : RecordRef;
      FieldsRef@1000000007 : FieldRef;
      OutStr@1000000004 : OutStream;
      Bytes@1000000003 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
      MimeType@1000000005 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      ErrNotAllowedToAttach@1000000008 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to attach a document. Please contact your administrator.';
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      TESTFIELD(Archived, FALSE);
      CALCFIELDS(Type);
      IF UserSetupManagement.GetEmployeeNo <> '' THEN BEGIN
        IF Type IN [Type::"Travel Ticket", Type::"Letter of Guarantee",Type::Visa] THEN
          ERROR(ErrNotAllowedToAttach, Type);
      END;

      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      IF (Base64TextToBlob = '') AND (NOT Attachment.HASVALUE) THEN
        EXIT;

      IF Base64TextToBlob = '' THEN BEGIN
        CLEAR(Attachment);
        CLEAR("File Extension");
        CLEAR("Has Attachment");
        MODIFY;
      END;

      Bytes := Convert.FromBase64String(Base64TextToBlob);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream(Bytes);
      Attachment.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      MemoryStream.WriteTo(OutStr);
      "Has Attachment" := TRUE;
      IF ("Employee No." <> '') AND ("Line No." <> 0) THEN BEGIN
        MODIFY;
        ArchiveEmployeeQualification;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetAttachment@1000000013() : Text;
    VAR
      BlobToBase64Txt@1000000004 : Text;
      InStr@1000000003 : InStream;
      Bytes@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN
       // PHP Start
       BlobToBase64Txt := '';
       CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
       IF NOT Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);

       Attachment.CREATEINSTREAM(InStr);
       MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream();
       COPYSTREAM(MemoryStream, InStr);
       Bytes := MemoryStream.GetBuffer();
       BlobToBase64Txt := Convert.ToBase64String(Bytes);
       EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);
    END;

    PROCEDURE ImportAttachment@1000000022();
    VAR
      ErrNotAllowedToAttach@1000000008 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to attach a document. Please contact your administrator.';
      ErrChangeAttachment@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=Do you want to change the attachment?';
      TempBlob@1000000002 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      FileManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 419;
      ImportTxt@1000000006 : TextConst 'ENU=Select a file to import';
      FileFilterTxt@1000000005 : TextConst '@@@=Do not translate the file extensions (e.g. .xml, .txt, .csv, etc);ENU="PDF Files(*.pdf)|*.pdf|Image Files(*.jpeg;*.png;*.gif;*.svg)|*.jpeg;*.png;*.gif;*.svg"';
      FileFilterExtensionTxt@1000000004 : TextConst '@@@={Locked};ENU=pdf,jpeg,png,gif,svg';
      FilePath@1000000007 : Text;
      FileExtension@1000000003 : Text;
    BEGIN
       // PHP Start
       TESTFIELD(Archived, FALSE);
       CALCFIELDS(Type);
       IF UserSetupManagement.GetEmployeeNo <> '' THEN BEGIN
        IF Type IN [Type::"Travel Ticket", Type::"Letter of Guarantee", Type::Visa] THEN
          ERROR(ErrNotAllowedToAttach, Type);
       END;

       CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
       IF Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        IF NOT CONFIRM(ErrChangeAttachment,FALSE) THEN
          EXIT;
        FilePath := FileManagement.BLOBImportWithFilter(TempBlob, ImportTxt, '',FileFilterTxt, FileFilterExtensionTxt);
       IF FilePath = '' THEN
        EXIT;
       TempBlob.INSERT;

       FileExtension := FileManagement.GetExtension(FilePath);
       TempBlob.CALCFIELDS(Blob);

       VALIDATE("File Extension", FileExtension);
       TESTFIELD("File Extension");

       Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
       "Has Attachment" := TRUE;
       MODIFY;
       ArchiveEmployeeQualification;
    END;

    PROCEDURE ExportAttachment@5(UseDialog@1002 : Boolean) : Text;
    VAR
      TempBlob@1000 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      FileMgt@1001 : Codeunit 419;
      OutStream@1004 : OutStream;
      FileName@1003 : Text;
    BEGIN
       // PHP Start
       CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
       IF NOT Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT;

       FileName := Description + '.' + "File Extension";

       TempBlob.INIT;
       TempBlob.Blob := Attachment;
       TempBlob.INSERT;
       TempBlob.Blob.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStream);

       EXIT(FileMgt.BLOBExport(TempBlob,FileName,UseDialog));
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetDocumentExpiryDates@1000000014(FieldNos@1000000000 : Integer);
    VAR
      ErrMustNotBeEarlier@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 must not be earlier than %2, currert value is %3.';
      ErrMustBeEarlier@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 must be earlier than %2, currert value is %3.';
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      CASE FieldNos OF
        FIELDNO("From Date"):
          BEGIN
            Qualification.GET("Qualification Code");
            IF FORMAT(Qualification."Calculate Expiry") = '' THEN
              EXIT;

            TESTFIELD("From Date");

            IF "From Date" = 0D THEN
              "From Date" := TODAY;
            IF "To Date" = 0D THEN
              "To Date":= CALCDATE(Qualification."Calculate Expiry", "From Date");
            IF "Expiration Date" = 0D THEN
              "Expiration Date" := "To Date";

            IF "From Date" > TODAY THEN
              ERROR( ErrMustNotBeEarlier, FIELDNAME("From Date"), TODAY, "From Date");
          END;
        FIELDNO("To Date"):
          BEGIN
            Qualification.GET("Qualification Code");
            IF FORMAT(Qualification."Calculate Expiry") = '' THEN
              EXIT;

            SetDocumentExpiryDates(0);

          END;
        ELSE BEGIN
          IF Qualification.GET("Qualification Code") AND (FORMAT(Qualification."Calculate Expiry") <> '') THEN BEGIN
            TESTFIELD("From Date");
            TESTFIELD("To Date");
            IF "From Date" > TODAY THEN
              ERROR( ErrMustNotBeEarlier, FIELDNAME("From Date"), TODAY, "From Date");
            IF "To Date" < TODAY THEN
              ERROR(ErrMustBeEarlier, FIELDNAME("To Date"), TODAY, "To Date");
          END;
        END;
      END;
      // PHP End
    END;

    PROCEDURE ArchiveEmployeeQualification@1000000003();
    VAR
      EmployeeQualification2@1000000003 : Record 5203;
      TempEmployeeQualification@1000000002 : TEMPORARY Record 5203;
      ArchiveEmployeeQualification@1000000001 : Record 5203;
      LineNo@1000000000 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      HumanResourcesSetup.GET;
      IF HumanResourcesSetup."Archive Employee Qualification" THEN BEGIN
        LineNo := 10000;
        // Get the Last No of Employee Qualification
        EmployeeQualification2.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "Employee No.");
        IF EmployeeQualification2.FINDLAST THEN
          LineNo += EmployeeQualification2."Line No.";

        TempEmployeeQualification := Rec;
        Rec.CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
        ArchiveEmployeeQualification.INIT;
        ArchiveEmployeeQualification.TRANSFERFIELDS(TempEmployeeQualification);
        ArchiveEmployeeQualification.CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
        ArchiveEmployeeQualification.Attachment := Rec.Attachment;
        CLEAR(ArchiveEmployeeQualification."Line No.");
        ArchiveEmployeeQualification."Line No." := LineNo;
        ArchiveEmployeeQualification.Archived := TRUE;
        ArchiveEmployeeQualification.INSERT;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetLastNo@1000000000() : Integer;
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      IF FINDLAST THEN
        EXIT("Line No.")
      ELSE
        EXIT(0);
      // PHP End
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

    { 50010;  ;Include in Utilization;Boolean     ;FieldClass=FlowField;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE CalcBaseQty@14(Qty@1000 : Decimal) : Decimal;
    BEGIN
      TESTFIELD("Qty. per Unit of Measure");
      EXIT(ROUND(Qty * "Qty. per Unit of Measure",0.00001));
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }

  {
    VAR
      EmployeeAbsence@1001 : Record 5207;
      HumanResUnitOfMeasure@1000 : Record 5220;
      Text001@1002 : TextConst 'ENU=You cannot change %1 because there are %2.';
      Deadline@1000000000 : Date;

    PROCEDURE CheckExpenseClaimCutoff@1000000006();
    VAR
      CompanyInfo@1000000008 : Record 79;
      HumanResourcesSetup@1000000000 : Record 5218;
      CalendarMgt@1000000005 : Codeunit 7600;
      PayrollDate@1000000002 : Date;
      Err01@1000000003 : TextConst 'ENU=Expense claim must not be later than %1.';
      AdjustedPayrollDate@1000000007 : Date;
      ExpenseClaimDeadline@1000000009 : Date;
      AdjustedExpenseClaimDate@1000000001 : Date;
    BEGIN
      HumanResourcesSetup.GET;
      HumanResourcesSetup.TESTFIELD("Payroll Cutoff");
      HumanResourcesSetup.TESTFIELD("Expense Claim Cutoff");

      // Get the paryoll date adjust if weekends and holidays.
      PayrollDate := CALCDATE(HumanResourcesSetup."Payroll Cutoff", TODAY);
      AdjustedPayrollDate := CalculateDates(PayrollDate);

      // Get the expense claim filing deadline adjust if weekends and holidays.
      ExpenseClaimDeadline := CALCDATE(HumanResourcesSetup."Expense Claim Cutoff",AdjustedPayrollDate);
      AdjustedExpenseClaimDate := CalculateDates(ExpenseClaimDeadline);

      IF TODAY > AdjustedExpenseClaimDate THEN
        ERROR(Err01, AdjustedExpenseClaimDate);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE CalculateDates@1000000065(DateField@1000000000 : Date) : Date;
    VAR
      MonthyCutoff@1000000001 : Date;
      CompanyInfo@1000000002 : Record 79;
      HumanResourcesSetup@1000000003 : Record 5218;
      ExpenseClaimDeadline@1000000004 : Date;
      StartingDate@1000000005 : Date;
      CalendarMgt@1000000006 : Codeunit 7600;
      DateDscr@1000000007 : Text;
      CutoffField@1000000008 : Date;
      ValidDate@1000000009 : Date;
      VarDate@1000000010 : Date;
    BEGIN
      CompanyInfo.GET;
      CompanyInfo.TESTFIELD("Base Calendar Code");

      IF CalendarMgt.CheckDateStatus(CompanyInfo."Base Calendar Code",DateField,DateDscr) THEN
        REPEAT
          DateField -= 1;
        UNTIL NOT CalendarMgt.CheckDateStatus(CompanyInfo."Base Calendar Code", DateField,DateDscr);
      EXIT (DateField);
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

                                                                StringPos@1000 : Integer;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                // PHP Start
                                                                "Middle Initial" := DELCHR("Middle Initial", '=', ' .');
                                                                IF "Middle Initial" <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                                                  StringPos := STRPOS("Middle Initial", '.') - 1;
                                                                  IF StringPos < 1 THEN
                                                                    "Middle Initial" := UPPERCASE("Middle Initial" + '.')
