  {
    VAR
      HumanResSetup@1000 : Record 5218;
      Applicant@1001 : Record 59010;
      PostCode@1003 : Record 225;
      NoSeriesMgt@1012 : Codeunit 396;
      DimMgt@1015 : Codeunit 408;
      Text000@1016 : TextConst 'ENU=Before you can use Online Map, you must fill in the Online Map Setup window.\See Setting Up Online Map in Help.';
      Text001@1017 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 of %2 has been successfully updated to %3 in %4.';
      Err01@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=The email address is already in used. Please select an different email address.';
      Err02@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=Please indicate at least one (1) Character Reference.';
      Err03@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=Please indicate at least one (1) Experience.';
      Err04@1000000003 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 must not be later than %2. Current value is %3.';
      UserSetupManagement@1000000004 : Codeunit 5700;
      Err05@1000000005 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to change the %1 from %2 to %3. Please contact your system administrator.';

    LOCAL PROCEDURE InitInsert@1000000002();
    BEGIN
      IF "No." = '' THEN BEGIN
        HumanResSetup.GET;
        HumanResSetup.TESTFIELD("Applicant Nos.");
        NoSeriesMgt.InitSeries(HumanResSetup."Applicant Nos.",xRec."No. Series",0D,"No.","No. Series");
      END;

      InitRecord;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE InitRecord@1000000001();
    BEGIN
      IF "Date Registered" = 0D THEN
        "Date Registered" := TODAY;

      SetBasicQualifications;
    END;

    PROCEDURE AssistEdit@2(OldApplicant@1000 : Record 59010) : Boolean;
    BEGIN
      WITH Applicant DO BEGIN
        Applicant := Rec;
        HumanResSetup.GET;
        HumanResSetup.TESTFIELD("Applicant Nos.");
        IF NoSeriesMgt.SelectSeries(HumanResSetup."Applicant Nos.",OldApplicant."No. Series","No. Series") THEN BEGIN
          HumanResSetup.GET;
          HumanResSetup.TESTFIELD("Applicant Nos.");
          NoSeriesMgt.SetSeries("No.");
          Rec := Applicant;
          EXIT(TRUE);
        END;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestRegistration@1000000005();
    BEGIN
      // Registration required field
      TESTFIELD("First Name");
      TESTFIELD("Birth Date");
      TESTFIELD(Gender);
      TESTFIELD("HR-Question 1");
      TESTFIELD("Birth Date");
      TESTFIELD("Country/Region Code");
      TESTFIELD("E-Mail");
      TESTFIELD("HR-Question 2");
    END;

    PROCEDURE FullName@1() : Text[100];
    BEGIN
      IF "Middle Initial" = '' THEN
        EXIT("First Name" + ' ' + "Last Name");
      EXIT("First Name" + ' ' + "Middle Initial" + ' ' + "Last Name");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE Stepper@1000000008();
    VAR
      ApplicantCharacterReference@1000000001 : Record 59027;
      ApplicantJobHistory@1000000000 : Record 59028;
    BEGIN
      CASE Step OF
        1: // Personal Profile
          BEGIN
            TESTFIELD("Current Rank Code");
            TESTFIELD("First Name");
            TESTFIELD("Birth Date");
            TESTFIELD(Gender);
            TESTFIELD("HR-Question 1");
            TESTFIELD("Birth Date");
            TESTFIELD("Country/Region Code");
            TESTFIELD("E-Mail");
            TESTFIELD("HR-Question 2");
            TESTFIELD(Address);
            TESTFIELD("Birth Date");
            TESTFIELD("Religion Code");
            TESTFIELD("Next of Kin Name");
            TESTFIELD("Next of Kin Relationship");
            TESTFIELD("Next of Kin Contact No.");
            TESTFIELD("Consent Accepted", TRUE);
          END;
        2: // Travel Documentation
          BEGIN
            // Part of Competency
            TESTFIELD("Date Graduated");
            TESTFIELD(University);
            TESTFIELD("Course/Degree");
            TestBasicQualifications;
          END;
        3: // Character Reference
          BEGIN
            ApplicantCharacterReference.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "No.");
            IF NOT ApplicantCharacterReference.FINDFIRST THEN
              ERROR(Err02);
          END;
        4:
          BEGIN
            ApplicantJobHistory.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "No.");
            IF NOT ApplicantJobHistory.FINDFIRST THEN
              ERROR(Err03);
            Status := Status::Registered;
          END;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ValidateShortcutDimCode@29(FieldNumber@1000 : Integer;VAR ShortcutDimCode@1001 : Code[20]);
    BEGIN
      DimMgt.ValidateDimValueCode(FieldNumber,ShortcutDimCode);
      DimMgt.SaveDefaultDim(DATABASE::Employee,"No.",FieldNumber,ShortcutDimCode);
      MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE DisplayMap@7();
    VAR
      MapPoint@1001 : Record 800;
      MapMgt@1000 : Codeunit 802;
    BEGIN
      IF MapPoint.FINDFIRST THEN
        MapMgt.MakeSelection(DATABASE::Employee,GETPOSITION)
      ELSE
        MESSAGE(Text000);
    END;

    PROCEDURE FormalName@8() : Text;
    VAR
      FName@1000 : Text;
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      IF ("Last Name" <> '') AND ("First Name" = '') THEN
        FName := "Last Name" + '';
      IF ("Last Name" = '') AND ("First Name" <> '') THEN
        FName := "First Name" + '';
      IF ("Last Name" <> '') AND ("First Name" <> '') AND ("Middle Initial" = '') THEN
        FName := "Last Name" + ', ' + "First Name";
      IF ("Last Name" <> '') AND ("First Name" <> '') THEN
        FName := "Last Name" + ', ' + "First Name" + ' ' + "Middle Initial";

      EXIT(UPPERCASE(FName));
      // PHP End
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetMiddleInitial@16();
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      IF "Middle Name" <> '' THEN BEGIN

      "Middle Initial" := UPPERCASE(COPYSTR("Middle Name",1,1)) + '.';
      END;
      // PHP End
    END;

    PROCEDURE InsertApplicantRegistration@1000000000();
    VAR
      Applcnt@1000000000 : Record 59010;
      User@1000000001 : Record 2000000120;
      UserSetup@1000000002 : Record 91;
      Err01@1000000003 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 already in used. Please use a different %1.';
      HumanResourcesSetup@1000000005 : Record 5218;
      UserCardPage@1000000004 : Page 9807;
    BEGIN
      HumanResourcesSetup.GET;
      HumanResourcesSetup.TESTFIELD("Enable Recruitment Process");
      HumanResourcesSetup.TESTFIELD("Default User Group Code");

      TESTFIELD("First Name");
      TESTFIELD(Gender);
      TESTFIELD("Country/Region Code");
      TESTFIELD("E-Mail");
      TESTFIELD("Birth Date");
      TESTFIELD("HR-Question 1");
      TESTFIELD("HR-Question 2");

      Applcnt.SETRANGE("E-Mail", "E-Mail");
      IF Applcnt.FINDFIRST THEN
        ERROR(Err01, "E-Mail", FIELDCAPTION("E-Mail"));
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetAge@1000000004() : Integer;
    VAR
      TempAge@1000000000 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      TempAge := 0;
      IF "Birth Date" = 0D THEN
        EXIT(TempAge);

      TempAge := DATE2DMY(TODAY, 3) - DATE2DMY("Birth Date", 3);
      IF TempAge <= 0 THEN
        EXIT(0);

      IF CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1Y>',TempAge),"Birth Date") > TODAY THEN
          TempAge -= 1;

      EXIT(TempAge);
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetQualificationPerPosition@1000000003();
    VAR
      ApplicantQualification@1000000001 : Record 59019;
      DefaultQualificationValues@1000000000 : Record 59031;
    BEGIN
      // Set the applicant qualification based on the Position
      IF ("Current Rank Code" <> '') AND ("Current Rank Code" <> xRec."Current Rank Code") THEN BEGIN
        DefaultQualificationValues.SETRANGE("Table ID", DATABASE::Position);
        DefaultQualificationValues.SETRANGE("No.", "Current Rank Code");
        IF DefaultQualificationValues.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
          REPEAT
            IF NOT ApplicantQualification.GET("No.", DefaultQualificationValues."Qualification Code") THEN BEGIN
              ApplicantQualification.INIT;
              ApplicantQualification."Applicant No." := "No.";
              ApplicantQualification.VALIDATE("Qualification Code", DefaultQualificationValues."Qualification Code");
              ApplicantQualification."Position Code" := "Current Rank Code";
              ApplicantQualification.INSERT;
            END;
          UNTIL DefaultQualificationValues.NEXT = 0;
        END;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetBasicQualifications@1000000009();
    VAR
      BasicQualificationSetup@1000000000 : Record 59031;
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000001 : Record 59019;
    BEGIN
      BasicQualificationSetup.SETRANGE("Table ID", 0);
      BasicQualificationSetup.SETFILTER("No.", '''''');
      IF BasicQualificationSetup.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          IF NOT ApplicantQualifications.GET("No.", BasicQualificationSetup."Qualification Code") THEN BEGIN
            ApplicantQualifications.INIT;
            ApplicantQualifications."Applicant No." := "No.";
            ApplicantQualifications."Qualification Code" := BasicQualificationSetup."Qualification Code";
            ApplicantQualifications.INSERT;
          END;
        UNTIL BasicQualificationSetup.NEXT = 0;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetStatus@1000000014(NewStatus@1000000000 : Integer);
    BEGIN
      CASE NewStatus OF
        Status::"Complete Registration", Status::Registered:;
        ELSE BEGIN
          IF UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '' THEN
            ERROR(Err05, FIELDCAPTION(Status), xRec.Status, Status);
          Step := 0;
        END;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestBasicQualifications@1000000010();
    VAR
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000000 : Record 59019;
      Qualification@1000000001 : Record 5202;
    BEGIN
      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "No.");
      IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          Qualification.GET(ApplicantQualifications."Qualification Code");
          IF FORMAT(Qualification."Calculate Expiry") <> '' THEN BEGIN
            ApplicantQualifications.TESTFIELD("From Date");
            ApplicantQualifications.TESTFIELD("To Date");
            ApplicantQualifications.TESTFIELD("Document No.");
          END;
          ApplicantQualifications.CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
          IF NOT ApplicantQualifications.Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
            ApplicantQualifications.TESTFIELD(Attachment);
        UNTIL ApplicantQualifications.NEXT = 0;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE CompleteProfileRegistration@1000000013();
    BEGIN
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetPicture@1000000006(PictureTxt@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      OutStr@1000000004 : OutStream;
      Bytes@1000000003 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN
      IF PictureTxt = '' THEN BEGIN
        CALCFIELDS(Picture);
        CLEAR(Picture);
        MODIFY;
        EXIT;
      END;

      Bytes := Convert.FromBase64String(PictureTxt);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream(Bytes);
      Picture.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      MemoryStream.WriteTo(OutStr);

      MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetPicture@1000000007(VAR PictureTxt@1000000004 : Text);
    VAR
      InStr@1000000003 : InStream;
      Bytes@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS(Picture);
      IF NOT Picture.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT;

      Picture.CREATEINSTREAM(InStr);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream();
      COPYSTREAM(MemoryStream, InStr);
      Bytes := MemoryStream.GetBuffer();
      PictureTxt := Convert.ToBase64String(Bytes);
    END;

    PROCEDURE TransferApplicantToEmployee@1000000011(VAR JobApplication@1000000017 : Record 59025);
    VAR
      Employee@1000000011 : Record 5200;
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000004 : Record 59019;
      EmpQualification@1000000005 : Record 5203;
      ApplicantCharReference@1000000006 : Record 59027;
      EmpCharReference@1000000007 : Record 59035;
      ApplicantJobHistory@1000000009 : Record 59028;
      EmpSeaServiceRecord@1000000010 : Record 59034;
      User@1000000002 : Record 2000000120;
      HumanResourcesSetup@1000000012 : Record 5218;
      UserSetup@1000000014 : Record 91;
      ResponsibilityCenter@1000000003 : Record 5714;
      UserGroupMember@1000000016 : Record 9001;
      IdentityManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 9801;
      EmpQualificationLineNo@1000000008 : Integer;
      ErrEmployeeExist@1000000013 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 %2 already exist.Process has been terminated. Please contact your administrator.';
      ErrNoUserFound@1000000015 : TextConst 'ENU="User with an E-Mail %1 is an invalid user. Please contact your administrator. "';
      ErrNoValidJobApplication@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 does not have a valid %2. Please complete at least one (1) application for %1.';
    BEGIN
      // PHP Start
      HumanResourcesSetup.GET;
      HumanResourcesSetup.TESTFIELD("Default User Group ESS Code");
      HumanResourcesSetup.TESTFIELD("Reset Password URL");

      CLEAR(Employee);
      Employee.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "No.");
      IF NOT Employee.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
        // Validation of Applicant and Job Application
      //  TESTFIELD(Status, Status::Registered);

        // Validate if there's an existing Job Application with hired status
        JobApplication.TESTFIELD(Status, JobApplication.Status::"Approved By Client");

        // Insert Employee
        Employee.INIT;
        Employee.TRANSFERFIELDS(Rec);
        CLEAR(Employee."No.");
        CLEAR(Employee.Picture);
        Employee."Applicant No." := "No.";
        Employee."Current Rank Code" := JobApplication."Position Code";
        Employee.CALCFIELDS(Picture);
        Rec.CALCFIELDS(Picture);
        Employee.Picture := Rec.Picture;
        Employee.INSERT(TRUE);

        // Insert Responsibility
        IF NOT ResponsibilityCenter.GET(Employee."No.") THEN BEGIN
          ResponsibilityCenter.INIT;
          ResponsibilityCenter.Code := Employee."No.";
          ResponsibilityCenter.VALIDATE(Name, FormalName);
          ResponsibilityCenter.INSERT(TRUE);
        END;

        // Insert Employee Qualification
        CLEAR(ApplicantQualifications);
        EmpQualificationLineNo := 0;
        ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "No.");
        IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
          REPEAT
            ApplicantQualifications.CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
            EmpQualification.INIT;
            EmpQualification.TRANSFERFIELDS(ApplicantQualifications);
            EmpQualificationLineNo += 10000;
            EmpQualification."Line No." := EmpQualificationLineNo;
            EmpQualification."Employee No." := Employee."No.";
            EmpQualification.VALIDATE("Qualification Code", ApplicantQualifications."Qualification Code");
            EmpQualification.CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
            EmpQualification.Attachment := ApplicantQualifications.Attachment;
            EmpQualification.INSERT;
          UNTIL ApplicantQualifications.NEXT = 0;
        END;

        // Insert Employee Character Reference
        CLEAR(ApplicantCharReference);
        ApplicantCharReference.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "No.");
        IF ApplicantCharReference.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
          REPEAT
            EmpCharReference.INIT;
            EmpCharReference.TRANSFERFIELDS(ApplicantCharReference);
            EmpCharReference."Employee No." := Employee."No.";
            EmpCharReference.INSERT;
          UNTIL ApplicantCharReference.NEXT = 0;
        END;

        //  Insert Employee Sea Service Record
        CLEAR(ApplicantJobHistory);
        ApplicantJobHistory.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "No.");
        IF ApplicantJobHistory.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
          REPEAT
            EmpSeaServiceRecord.INIT;
            EmpSeaServiceRecord.TRANSFERFIELDS(ApplicantJobHistory);
            EmpSeaServiceRecord."Employee No." := Employee."No.";
            EmpSeaServiceRecord.INSERT;
          UNTIL ApplicantJobHistory.NEXT = 0;
        END;

        // Create a User
        User.SETRANGE("User Name", "E-Mail");
        IF User.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          // Assign the Crew User Group for the hired applicant/user
          UserGroupMember.INIT;
          UserGroupMember."User Group Code" := HumanResourcesSetup."Default User Group ESS Code";
          UserGroupMember."User Security ID" := User."User Security ID";
          UserGroupMember."Company Name" := COMPANYNAME;
          UserGroupMember.INSERT(TRUE);

          CLEAR(UserGroupMember);
          UserGroupMember.SETRANGE("User Group Code", HumanResourcesSetup."Default User Group Code");
          UserGroupMember.SETRANGE("User Security ID", User."User Security ID");
          UserGroupMember.DELETEALL(TRUE);

          CLEAR(UserSetup);
          // Assign the Employee No.
          IF UserSetup.GET(User."User Name") THEN BEGIN
            UserSetup.VALIDATE("User Group Code", HumanResourcesSetup."Default User Group ESS Code");
            UserSetup.VALIDATE("Employee No.", Employee."No.");
            UserSetup.VALIDATE("Base Resp. Center", ResponsibilityCenter.Code);
            UserSetup."E-Mail" := Applicant."E-Mail";
            UserSetup.MODIFY(TRUE);
          END ELSE BEGIN
          // Assign the Crew User Group for the hired applicant/user
            UserSetup.INIT;
            UserSetup.VALIDATE("User ID", User."User Name");
            UserSetup.VALIDATE("User Group Code", HumanResourcesSetup."Default User Group ESS Code");
            UserSetup.VALIDATE("Employee No.", Employee."No.");
            UserSetup.VALIDATE("Base Resp. Center", ResponsibilityCenter.Code);
            UserSetup."E-Mail" := Applicant."E-Mail";
            UserSetup.INSERT(TRUE);
          END;
        END ELSE
          ERROR(ErrNoUserFound, "E-Mail");
      END ELSE
        ERROR(ErrEmployeeExist, Applicant.TABLECAPTION, "No.");
    END;

    BEGIN
    {
      Notes:
        Clarify if the Certificate Limitation can be set as dropdown
    }
    END.
  }
}

OBJECT Table 59017 Expense Claim
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=06/26/18;

    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }

  {
    OnInsert=VAR
               Employee@1000000000 : Record 5200;
             BEGIN
               HumanResourcesSetup.CheckExpenseClaimCutoff;

               TestDetails;
             END;

               ExpenseClaimLine@1000000000 : Record 59018;
             BEGIN
               ExpenseClaimLine.SETRANGE("Expense Claim No.", "No.");

             END;

                                                                IF "No." <> xRec."No." THEN BEGIN

                                                                  "No. Series" := '';

    { 90  ;Yes;Status              ;Option        ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                TestAdminRights;
                                                              END;

                                                   OptionCaptionML=ENU=Open,Released,Pending Approval;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetAttachment@1000000001() Base64TextToBlob : Text;
    VAR
      Convert@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      Bytes@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      MemoryStream@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
      OutStr@1000000003 : OutStream;
    BEGIN
      TestDetails;

      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      IF (Base64TextToBlob = '') AND (NOT Attachment.HASVALUE) THEN
        EXIT;

      IF Base64TextToBlob = '' THEN BEGIN
        CLEAR(Attachment);
        MODIFY;
      END;

      Bytes := Convert.FromBase64String(Base64TextToBlob);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream(Bytes);
      Attachment.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      MemoryStream.WriteTo(OutStr);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetAttachment@1000000002() : Text;
    VAR
      Bytes@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      InStr@1000000001 : InStream;
      BlobToBase64Txt@1000000002 : Text;
      Convert@1000000003 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000004 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN
      BlobToBase64Txt := '';
      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);

      IF NOT Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT( BlobToBase64Txt);

      Attachment.CREATEINSTREAM(InStr);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream();
      COPYSTREAM(MemoryStream, InStr);
      Bytes := MemoryStream.GetBuffer();
      BlobToBase64Txt := Convert.ToBase64String(Bytes);
      EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);
    END;

    PROCEDURE ImportAttachment@1000000003();
    VAR
      FilePath@1000000000 : Text;
      FileManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 419;
      TempBlob@1000000002 : Record 99008535;
      ErrChangeAttachment@1000000003 : TextConst 'ENU=Do you want to change the attachment?';
      ImportTxt@1000000004 : TextConst 'ENU=Select a file to import';
      FileFilterTxt@1000000005 : TextConst 'ENU="PDF Files(*.pdf)|*.pdf|Image Files(*.jpeg;*.png;*.gif;*.svg)|*.jpeg;*.png;*.gif;*.svg"';
      FileFilterExtensionTxt@1000000006 : TextConst 'ENU=pdf,jpeg,png,gif,svg';
      FileExtension@1000000007 : Text;
    BEGIN
      //TestDetails;
      IF UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '' THEN BEGIN

      END;

      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      IF Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        IF NOT CONFIRM(ErrChangeAttachment, FALSE) THEN
          EXIT;
        FilePath := FileManagement.BLOBImportWithFilter(TempBlob, ImportTxt, '',FileFilterTxt, FileFilterExtensionTxt);
      IF FilePath = '' THEN
        EXIT;
      TempBlob.INSERT;

      FileExtension := FileManagement.GetExtension(FilePath);
      TempBlob.CALCFIELDS(Blob);

      VALIDATE("File Extension", FileExtension);
      TESTFIELD("File Extension");

      Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
      "Has Attachment" := TRUE;

      MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE ExportAttachment@1000000004(UseDialog@1000000004 : Boolean) : Text;
    VAR
      TempBlob@1000000000 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      FileMgt@1000000001 : Codeunit 419;
      OutStream@1000000002 : OutStream;
      FileName@1000000003 : Text;
      ExportSuccess@1000000005 : Boolean;
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      IF NOT Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT;

        FileName := Details + '.' + "File Extension";

        TempBlob.INIT;
        TempBlob.Blob := Attachment;
        TempBlob.INSERT;

        EXIT(FileMgt.BLOBExport(TempBlob,FileName,UseDialog));
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestDetails@1000000006();
    BEGIN
      // For Deletion
      IF (Details <> '') THEN
          ERROR('Details must be empty before deletion.');
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestExpenseClaimHeader@1000000000();
    VAR
      ExpenseClaim@1000000000 : Record 59017;
    BEGIN
      IF ExpenseClaim.GET("Expense Claim No.") THEN
        ExpenseClaim.TestAdminRights;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

      Err02@1000000003 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed the change the status from %1 to %2. Please contact your administrator.';
      Err03@1000000005 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to insert a document with a type %1. Please contact your administrator.';
      Err04@1000000006 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to delete a document with a type %1. Please contact your administrator.';
      Err05@1000000007 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to modify a document with a type %1. Please contact your administrator.';
      FileExtensionText@1000000004 : TextConst '@@@={Locked};ENU=pdf,jpeg,png,gif,svg';
      ErrNotAllowedToAttach@1000000008 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to attach a document. Please contact your administrator.';

    PROCEDURE InsertQualificationFromDefaultQualifications@1000000002(VAR JobApplication@1000000002 : Record 59025;VAR DefaultQualificationValues@1000000000 : Record 59031);
    VAR
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000001 : Record 59019;
    BEGIN
      WITH DefaultQualificationValues DO BEGIN
        IF ApplicantQualifications.GET(JobApplication."Applicant No.", DefaultQualificationValues."Qualification Code") THEN
          EXIT;

        ApplicantQualifications.INIT;
        ApplicantQualifications."Applicant No." := JobApplication."Applicant No.";
        ApplicantQualifications.VALIDATE("Qualification Code", DefaultQualificationValues."Qualification Code");

        // Check if whether the Table ID of Default Qualifications is Position or Vessel
        IF DefaultQualificationValues."Table ID" = DATABASE::Vessel THEN
          ApplicantQualifications.VALIDATE("Vessel Code", DefaultQualificationValues."No.");

        IF DefaultQualificationValues."Table ID" = DATABASE::Position THEN
          ApplicantQualifications.VALIDATE("Position Code", DefaultQualificationValues."No.");

        ApplicantQualifications.INSERT;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE InsertQualificationFromQualification@1000000009(Qualification@1000000000 : Record 5202;JobApplication@1000000001 : Record 59025);
    BEGIN
      IF NOT GET(JobApplication."Applicant No.",Qualification.Code) THEN BEGIN
        INIT;
        "Applicant No." := JobApplication."Applicant No.";
        "Qualification Code" := Qualification.Code;

        IF Qualification.Type = Qualification.Type::"Travel Ticket" THEN BEGIN
          "From Date" := JobApplication."Date of Departure";
          "To Date" := JobApplication."Date of Departure";
        END;

        IF Qualification.Type = Qualification.Type::"Letter of Guarantee" THEN BEGIN
          "From Date" := TODAY;
          "To Date" := TODAY;
        END;

        INSERT;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestDocumentType@1000000008();
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS(Type);
      IF UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '' THEN
        IF Type IN [Type::"Offer Letter", Type::Contract, Type::"Travel Ticket",
            Type::"Letter of Guarantee", Type::Visa] THEN
          ERROR(Err05, Type);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestQualifications@1000000001();
    VAR
      ErrPartOfBasicQualification@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to delete the %1 %2 %3. It''s part of %4.';
      DefaultQualificationValues@1000000000 : Record 59031;
      JobApplication@1000000002 : Record 59025;
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000003 : Record 59019;
      ErrContractDocuments@1000000004 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to delete the document %1.';
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS(Description);
      IF ("Position Code" = '') AND ("Vessel Code" = '') AND
          (DefaultQualificationValues.GET(0, '',"Qualification Code")) THEN
        ERROR(ErrPartOfBasicQualification, Rec.TABLECAPTION, "Qualification Code", Description,
          DefaultQualificationValues.TABLECAPTION);

      IF ("Position Code" <> '') AND ("Vessel Code" = '') AND
        (DefaultQualificationValues.GET(DATABASE::Position, "Position Code","Qualification Code")) THEN
        ERROR(ErrPartOfBasicQualification, Rec.TABLECAPTION, "Qualification Code", Description,
          DefaultQualificationValues.TABLECAPTION);

      IF ("Position Code" = '') AND ("Vessel Code" <> '') AND
        (DefaultQualificationValues.GET(DATABASE::Vessel, "Position Code","Qualification Code")) THEN
        ERROR(ErrPartOfBasicQualification, Rec.TABLECAPTION, "Qualification Code", Description,
          DefaultQualificationValues.TABLECAPTION);
    END;

    PROCEDURE TestInitValues@1000000003();
    BEGIN
      TESTFIELD("From Date");
      TESTFIELD("To Date");
      TESTFIELD("Document No.");
      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      IF Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        TESTFIELD("File Extension");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestAcceptanceOfContracts@1000000004();
    BEGIN
      // For Deletion
      TESTFIELD("Offer Letter Accepted", FALSE);
      TESTFIELD("Contract Accepted", FALSE);
    END;

    PROCEDURE ValidateApplicantQualifications@1000000005(ApplicantNo@1000000000 : Code[20]);
    VAR
      Applicant@1000000001 : Record 59010;
      ErrNoAttachment@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=Attachment must have a value in %1.';
    BEGIN
      Applicant.GET(ApplicantNo);
      SETRANGE("Applicant No.", Applicant."No.");
      IF FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          Qualification.GET("Qualification Code");
          IF FORMAT(Qualification."Calculate Expiry") <> '' THEN BEGIN
            TESTFIELD("Document No.");
            TESTFIELD("From Date");
            TESTFIELD("To Date");
          END;
          CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
          IF NOT Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
            ERROR(ErrNoAttachment, FORMAT(RECORDID));
        UNTIL NEXT = 0;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetFilterForApplicant@1000000000();
    VAR
      UserSetupManagement@1000000000 : Codeunit 5700;
    BEGIN
      IF UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '' THEN BEGIN
        FILTERGROUP(2);
        SETRANGE("Applicant No.", UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo);
        FILTERGROUP(0);
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE ChangeStatusOfApplicantQualifications@1000000007(ApplicantNo@1000000001 : Code[20];AQStatus@1000000002 : Option);
    VAR
      Applicant@1000000000 : Record 59010;
    BEGIN
      Applicant.GET(ApplicantNo);
      SETRANGE("Applicant No.", Applicant."No.");
      // SETRANGE(Type, Type::" ");
      IF FINDSET THEN
        REPEAT
          VALIDATE(Status, AQStatus);
          MODIFY(TRUE);
        UNTIL NEXT = 0;
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetAttachment@1000000006(Base64TextToBlob@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      RecRef@1000000006 : RecordRef;
      FieldsRef@1000000007 : FieldRef;
      OutStr@1000000004 : OutStream;
      Bytes@1000000003 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
      MimeType@1000000005 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
    BEGIN
      TestAcceptanceOfContracts;
      CALCFIELDS(Type);
      IF UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '' THEN BEGIN
        IF Type IN [Type::"Travel Ticket", Type::"Letter of Guarantee",Type::Visa] THEN
          ERROR(ErrNotAllowedToAttach, Type);
      END;

      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      IF (Base64TextToBlob = '') AND (NOT Attachment.HASVALUE) THEN
        EXIT;

      IF Base64TextToBlob = '' THEN BEGIN
        CLEAR(Attachment);
        CLEAR("File Extension");
        CLEAR("Has Attachment");
        MODIFY;
      END;

      Bytes := Convert.FromBase64String(Base64TextToBlob);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream(Bytes);
      Attachment.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      MemoryStream.WriteTo(OutStr);
      "Has Attachment" := TRUE;
      //  Causing an error due to Delayed Insert. Working on Web Service
      // IF ("Applicant No." <> '') AND ("Qualification Code" <> '') THEN
      //  MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetAttachment@1000000013() : Text;
    VAR
      BlobToBase64Txt@1000000004 : Text;
      InStr@1000000003 : InStream;
      Bytes@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";

      COPYSTREAM(MemoryStream, InStr);
      Bytes := MemoryStream.GetBuffer();
      BlobToBase64Txt := Convert.ToBase64String(Bytes);

    PROCEDURE ImportAttachment@1000000022();
    VAR
      ErrChangeAttachment@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=Do you want to change the attachment?';
      TempBlob@1000000002 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      FileManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 419;

      FileFilterTxt@1000000005 : TextConst '@@@=Do not translate the file extensions (e.g. .xml, .txt, .csv, etc);ENU="PDF Files(*.pdf)|*.pdf|Image Files(*.jpeg;*.png;*.gif;*.svg)|*.jpeg;*.png;*.gif;*.svg"';

        IF Type IN [Type::"Travel Ticket", Type::"Letter of Guarantee", Type::Visa] THEN

        EXIT;

      VALIDATE("File Extension", FileExtension);
      TESTFIELD("File Extension");

      Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
      "Has Attachment" := TRUE;
      MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE ExportAttachment@5(UseDialog@1002 : Boolean) : Text;
    VAR
      TempBlob@1000 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      FileMgt@1001 : Codeunit 419;
      OutStream@1004 : OutStream;
      FileName@1003 : Text;
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      IF NOT Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT;

       CALCFIELDS(Description);
       FileName := Description + '.' + "File Extension";

       CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
       TempBlob.INIT;
       TempBlob.Blob := Attachment;
       TempBlob.INSERT;
       TempBlob.Blob.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStream);

       EXIT(FileMgt.BLOBExport(TempBlob,FileName,UseDialog));
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetDocumentExpiryDates@1000000014(FieldNos@1000000000 : Integer);
    BEGIN
      CASE FieldNos OF
        FIELDNO("From Date"):
          BEGIN
            Qualification.GET("Qualification Code");
            IF FORMAT(Qualification."Calculate Expiry") = '' THEN
              EXIT;

            TESTFIELD("From Date");

            IF "From Date" = 0D THEN
              "From Date" := TODAY;
            IF "To Date" = 0D THEN
              "To Date":= CALCDATE(Qualification."Calculate Expiry", "From Date");
            IF "Expiration Date" = 0D THEN
              "Expiration Date" := "To Date";

      //      IF "From Date" = 0D THEN BEGIN
      //        CLEAR("To Date");
      //        CLEAR("Expiration Date");
      //        EXIT;
      //      END;

            IF "From Date" > TODAY THEN
              ERROR( Err01, FIELDNAME("From Date"), TODAY, "From Date");
          END;
        FIELDNO("To Date"):
          BEGIN
            Qualification.GET("Qualification Code");
            IF FORMAT(Qualification."Calculate Expiry") = '' THEN
              EXIT;

            SetDocumentExpiryDates(0);

          END;
        ELSE BEGIN
          IF Qualification.GET("Qualification Code") AND (FORMAT(Qualification."Calculate Expiry") <> '') THEN BEGIN
            TESTFIELD("From Date");
            TESTFIELD("To Date");
            IF "From Date" > TODAY THEN
              ERROR( Err01, FIELDNAME("From Date"), TODAY, "From Date");
            IF "To Date" < TODAY THEN
              ERROR(Err06, FIELDNAME("To Date"), TODAY, "To Date");
          END;
        END;
      END;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

OBJECT Table 59025 Job Application
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=06/27/18;
    Time=[ 7:48:24 PM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    Permissions=TableData 1511=rimd,
                TableData 1514=rim;
    DataCaptionFields=Line No.;
    OnInsert=BEGIN
               TestJobApplication;
               Date := WORKDATE;
             END;

    OnModify=BEGIN
               IF Status = Status::Interviewing THEN
                 TestInterviewSchedule("Date of Interview", "Time of Interview");
             END;

    OnDelete=VAR
               InterviewSchedule@1000000000 : Record 59033;
             BEGIN
               InterviewSchedule.SETCURRENTKEY("Job Application No.", "Applicant No.");
               InterviewSchedule.SETRANGE("Job Application No.", "Line No.");
               InterviewSchedule.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "Applicant No.");
               InterviewSchedule.DELETEALL;
             END;

    DrillDownPageID=Page59025;
  }
  FIELDS
  {
    { 10  ;   ;Line No.            ;Integer       ;AutoIncrement=Yes;
                                                   Editable=No }
    { 15  ;   ;Applicant No.       ;Code20        ;TableRelation=Applicant;
                                                   OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                IF ("Applicant No." <> xRec."Applicant No.") AND (xRec."Applicant No." <> '') THEN
                                                                  FIELDERROR("Applicant No.");
                                                                TestStatusLockApplication;
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 20  ;   ;Position Code       ;Code10        ;TableRelation=Position;
                                                   OnValidate=VAR
                                                                Position@1000000000 : Record 59013;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                Position.GET("Position Code");
                                                                Description := Position.Position;
                                                                TestStatusLockApplication;
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 30  ;   ;Description         ;Text50         }
    { 40  ;   ;Status              ;Option        ;InitValue=Pending Application;
                                                   OnValidate=VAR
                                                                ApplicantQualifications@1000000007 : Record 59019;
                                                                JobQualification@1000000002 : Record 59026;
                                                                NotificationEntry@1000000003 : Record 1511;
                                                                UserSetup@1000000005 : Record 91;
                                                                Applicant@1000000006 : Record 59010;
                                                                ErrStatusPermission@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=You do not have the permission to change the status of your application from %1 to %2. Please contact your administrator.';
                                                                ErrCancelApplication@1000000004 : TextConst 'ENU=You are allowed to cancel your application when the status is in %1 stage.';
                                                                UserSetupManagement@1000000000 : Codeunit 5700;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                // Active Status: Pending Application, Interviewing, Under Review, Not Approved By Client, Approved By Client
                                                                CASE Status OF
                                                                  Status::"Pending Application":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      TestJobApplication;
                                                                      IF (UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '') AND NOT (xRec.Status IN [Status::"Pending Application",
                                                                          Status::"Application Submitted", Status::"Cancelled Application" ]) THEN BEGIN
                                                                        ERROR(ErrStatusPermission, xRec.Status, Status);
                                                                      END;
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Cancelled Application":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      IF (UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '') AND NOT (xRec.Status IN [Status::"Pending Application",
                                                                          Status::"Application Submitted" ]) THEN
                                                                        ERROR(ErrStatusPermission, xRec.Status, Status);
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Application Submitted":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      IF (UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '') AND NOT (xRec.Status IN [Status::"Pending Application",
                                                                          Status::"Application Submitted", Status::"Cancelled Application" ]) THEN
                                                                        ERROR(ErrStatusPermission, xRec.Status, Status);

                                                                      ClearReceiveDetails;
                                                                      ClearInterviewDetails;
                                                                      ClearOfferDetails;
                                                                      ClearTravelDetails;
                                                                      ClearVisaDetails;
                                                                      TestJobApplication;

                                                                      TestApplicantQualification;

                                                                      // E-mail notification for new Job Application/Application Submitted
                                                                      HumanResourcesSetup.GET;
                                                                      IF HumanResourcesSetup."HR Coordinator" <> '' THEN
                                                                        NotificationEntry.CreateNew2(NotificationEntry.Type::"N-JobApp",
                                                                          HumanResourcesSetup."HR Coordinator",Rec,0,'','','','','New Job Application');
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::Shortlisted:
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      ClearInterviewDetails;
                                                                      ClearOfferDetails;
                                                                      ClearVisaDetails;

                                                                      TestApplicantPermission;
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Application Received", Status::"Under Review":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      ClearReceiveDetails;
                                                                      ClearInterviewDetails;
                                                                      ClearOfferDetails;
                                                                      ClearTravelDetails;
                                                                      ClearVisaDetails;
                                                                      TestApplicantPermission;
                                                                      SetReceivingDetails;
                                                                      Applicant.GET("Applicant No.");
                                                                      UserSetup.GET(Applicant."E-Mail");
                                                                      NotificationEntry.CreateNew2(NotificationEntry.Type::"N-JAAppRec",
                                                                        UserSetup."User ID",Rec,0,'','','','','Application Under Review');
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::Interviewing:
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      ClearOfferDetails;
                                                                      ClearTravelDetails;
                                                                      ClearVisaDetails;
                                                                      TestApplicantPermission;
                                                                      TestApplicantQualification;
                                                                      ApplicantQualifications.ChangeStatusOfApplicantQualifications("Applicant No.", ApplicantQualifications.Status::Validated);

                                                                //      Applicant.GET("Applicant No.");
                                                                //      UserSetup.GET(Applicant."E-Mail");
                                                                //      NotificationEntry.CreateNew2(NotificationEntry.Type::"N-JAppIntv",
                                                                //        UserSetup."User ID",Rec,0,'','','','','For Interview');
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Offer Extended":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      ClearTravelDetails;
                                                                      ClearVisaDetails;
                                                                      TestApplicantPermission;
                                                                      RemoveTravelTicketRequest;
                                                                      RemoveContract;
                                                                      RemovePPE;
                                                                      IF "Received By User ID" = '' THEN
                                                                        "Received By User ID" := USERID;
                                                                      "Oferred By User ID" := USERID;
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Vessel Code");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Start Date");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("End Date");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Expiry Date");

                                                                      "Lock Offer Details" := TRUE;
                                                                      GenerateOfferLetter;
                                                                      Applicant.GET("Applicant No.");
                                                                      UserSetup.GET(Applicant."E-Mail");
                                                                      NotificationEntry.CreateNew2(NotificationEntry.Type::"N-JAppOflt",
                                                                        UserSetup."User ID", Rec, 0,'','','','','Offer Letter');
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Negotiate Offer":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      xRec.TESTFIELD(Status, xRec.Status::"Offer Extended");
                                                                      ClearTravelDetails;
                                                                      ClearVisaDetails;
                                                                      RemoveApplicantOfferLetter;
                                                                      RemoveTravelTicketRequest;
                                                                      RemoveContract;
                                                                      RemovePPE;

                                                                      VALIDATE("Lock Offer Details", FALSE);
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Offer Accepted":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      xRec.TESTFIELD(Status, xRec.Status::"Offer Extended");
                                                                      // Check offer letter in the Applicant Qualification
                                                                      ClearTravelDetails;
                                                                      ClearVisaDetails;
                                                                      TestApplicantQualification;

                                                                      // Update the offer letter as accepted
                                                                      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "Applicant No.");
                                                                      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE(Type, ApplicantQualifications.Type::"Offer Letter");
                                                                      IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                                                        ApplicantQualifications.VALIDATE("Offer Letter Accepted", TRUE);
                                                                        ApplicantQualifications.MODIFY(TRUE);
                                                                      END;
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Contract Extended":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      xRec.TESTFIELD(Status, xRec.Status::"Offer Accepted"); // Prerequisite for offering a contract
                                                                      RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                                      ClearVisaDetails;
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Date of Departure");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Sign-On Date");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Sign-Off Date");
                                                                      TestApplicantQualification;
                                                                      GenerateContract;
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Contract Accepted":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      xRec.TESTFIELD(Status, xRec.Status::"Contract Extended"); // Prerequisite for accepting the contract
                                                                      TestApplicantQualification;

                                                                      // Update the offer letter as accepted
                                                                      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "Applicant No.");
                                                                      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE(Type, ApplicantQualifications.Type::Contract);
                                                                      IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                                                        ApplicantQualifications.VALIDATE("Contract Accepted", TRUE);
                                                                        ApplicantQualifications.MODIFY(TRUE);
                                                                      END;
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Travel Ticket Request":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      IF NOT (xRec.Status IN [xRec.Status::"Contract Accepted", xRec.Status::"Visa Request"]) THEN
                                                                        FIELDERROR(Status);
                                                                      ClearVisaDetails;
                                                                      TestApplicantPermission;
                                                                      TestApplicantQualification;
                                                                      GeneratePlaneTicketQualification;
                                                                      GeneratePPE;
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Date of Departure");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Sign-On Date");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Sign-Off Date");
                                                                      VALIDATE("Lock Travel Details", TRUE);
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Visa Request":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      xRec.TESTFIELD(Status, xRec.Status::"Travel Ticket Request");
                                                                      TestApplicantPermission;
                                                                      TestApplicantQualification;
                                                                      GenerateVisaRequest;
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Date of Departure");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Sign-On Date");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Sign-Off Date");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Departure Details 1");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Departure Details 2");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Departure Details 3");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Date of Arrival");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Arrival Details 1");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Arrival Details 2");
                                                                      TESTFIELD("Arrival Details 3");
                                                                      VALIDATE("Lock Travel Ticket Details");
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Approved By Client":
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                //      xRec.TESTFIELD(Status, xRec.Status::Interviewing);
                                                                      TestApplicantPermission;
                                                                      TestApplicantQualification;

                                                                      Applicant.GET("Applicant No.");
                                                                      Applicant.Status := Applicant.Status::"Approved By Client";
                                                                      Applicant.MODIFY;

                                                                      Applicant.TransferApplicantToEmployee(Rec);
                                                                    END;
                                                                  Status::"Not Approved By Client":
                                                                      BEGIN
                                                                        TestApplicantPermission;

                                                                        // Change the Status of Applicant
                                                                        Applicant.GET("Applicant No.");
                                                                        Applicant.Status := Applicant.Status::"For Pooling";
                                                                        Applicant.MODIFY;

                                                                        UserSetup.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "Applicant No.");
                                                                        IF UserSetup.FINDFIRST THEN
                                                                          NotificationEntry.CreateNew2(NotificationEntry.Type::"N-JAppRej",
                                                                            UserSetup."User ID",Rec,0,'','','','','Update on Your Job Application');
                                                                      END;
                                                                  ELSE
                                                                    BEGIN
                                                                      TestApplicantPermission;
                                                                    END;
                                                                END;
                                                              END;

                                                   OptionCaptionML=ENU=Pending Application,Application Submitted,Application Received,Under Review,Shortlisted,Interviewing,Assessment Stage,Offer Extended,Offer Accepted,Not Approved By Client,On Hold,Approved By Client,Cancelled Application,Pool,Contract Extended,Contract Accepted,Negotiate Offer,Travel Ticket Request,Visa Request,Contract Ended;
                                                   OptionString=Pending Application,Application Submitted,Application Received,Under Review,Shortlisted,Interviewing,Assessment Stage,Offer Extended,Offer Accepted,Not Approved By Client,On Hold,Approved By Client,Cancelled Application,Pool,Contract Extended,Contract Accepted,Negotiate Offer,Travel Ticket Request,Visa Request,Contract Ended }
    { 50  ;   ;Date                ;Date          ;Editable=No }
    { 59  ;   ;Date and Time Received;DateTime    ;Editable=No }
    { 60  ;   ;Received By User ID ;Code50        ;TableRelation="User Setup";
                                                   Editable=No }

                                                                  FIELDERROR(Status);

                                                                IF Status = Status::"Offer Extended" THEN
                                                                  FIELDERROR(Status);
                                                              END;

    { 95  ;   ;Lock Offer Details  ;Boolean       ;Editable=No }

                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 130 ;   ;Oferred By User ID  ;Code50        ;TableRelation="User Setup";
                                                   Editable=No }
    { 140 ;   ;First Name          ;Text50        ;FieldClass=FlowField;
                                                   CalcFormula=Lookup(Applicant."First Name" WHERE (No.=FIELD(Applicant No.)));
                                                   Editable=No }

                                                   CalcFormula=Lookup(Applicant."Last Name" WHERE (No.=FIELD(Applicant No.)));
                                                   Editable=No }

                                                   CalcFormula=Lookup(Applicant.E-Mail WHERE (No.=FIELD(Applicant No.)));
                                                   Editable=No }

                                                   CalcFormula=Lookup(Applicant.Age WHERE (No.=FIELD(Applicant No.)));
                                                   Editable=No }
    { 200 ;   ;Lock Travel Details ;Boolean       ;Editable=No }
    { 210 ;   ;Date of Departure   ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                                TESTFIELD("Lock Travel Details", FALSE);
                                                                IF "Date of Departure" < TODAY THEN
                                                                  ERROR(Err01, FIELDNAME("Date of Departure"), TODAY -1, "Date of Departure");

                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 211 ;   ;Departure Details 1 ;Code30        ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                TESTFIELD("Lock Travel Ticket Details", FALSE);

                                                                RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 212 ;   ;Departure Details 2 ;Code30        ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                TESTFIELD("Lock Travel Ticket Details", FALSE);

                                                                RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 213 ;   ;Departure Details 3 ;Code30        ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                TESTFIELD("Lock Travel Ticket Details", FALSE);

                                                                RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 220 ;   ;Sign-On Date        ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                                TESTFIELD("Lock Travel Details", FALSE);

                                                                IF "Sign-On Date" < TODAY THEN
                                                                  ERROR(Err01, FIELDNAME("Sign-On Date"), TODAY -1, "Sign-On Date");
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 230 ;   ;Sign-Off Date       ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                                TESTFIELD("Lock Travel Details", FALSE);
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 240 ;   ;Date of Arrival     ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                TESTFIELD("Lock Travel Ticket Details", FALSE);

                                                                RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 241 ;   ;Arrival Details 1   ;Code30        ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                TESTFIELD("Lock Travel Ticket Details", FALSE);

                                                                RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 242 ;   ;Arrival Details 2   ;Code30        ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                TESTFIELD("Lock Travel Ticket Details", FALSE);

                                                                RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 243 ;   ;Arrival Details 3   ;Code30        ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                TESTFIELD("Lock Travel Ticket Details", FALSE);

                                                                RestrictApplicantModification;
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 260 ;   ;Lock Travel Ticket Details;Boolean ;Editable=No }
  }
  KEYS
  {
    {    ;Line No.                                ;Clustered=Yes }
  }

    VAR
      Applicant@1000000000 : Record 59010;
      HumanResourcesSetup@1000000001 : Record 5218;
      OutStr@1000000002 : OutStream;

      Err02@1000000004 : TextConst 'ENU=Please setup a Qualification for the Type ''%1'' or contact your administrator.';
      Err03@1000000005 : TextConst 'ENU=Something went wrong in generating the the report. Please contact your administrator.';
      Err04@1000000006 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to modify the %1 when the %2 is %3.';

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestStatusLockApplication@1000000024();
    BEGIN
       IF Status IN [Status::"Approved By Client", Status::"Cancelled Application", Status::"Contract Ended"] THEN
        ERROR(Err04, FORMAT(Rec.RECORDID), FIELDNAME(Status), Status);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE RestrictApplicantModification@1000000018();
    VAR
      UserSetupManagement@1000000000 : Codeunit 5700;
      NotAllowedToEditErr@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=You do not have the permission to modify this record.';
    BEGIN
      IF UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '' THEN
        ERROR(NotAllowedToEditErr);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestJobApplication@1000000001();
    VAR
      JobApplication@1000000000 : Record 59025;
      ErrPendingApplication@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to create multiple job application. You have a pending application for the position of %1.';
    BEGIN
      GetApplicant;
      JobApplication.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", Applicant."No.");
      JobApplication.SETFILTER(Status, '<>%1&<>%2&<>%3',Status::"Cancelled Application", Status::"Not Approved By Client", Status::"Contract Ended");
      JobApplication.SETFILTER("Line No.", '<>%1', "Line No.");
      IF JobApplication.FINDFIRST THEN
        ERROR(ErrPendingApplication, JobApplication.Description);


      // TODO: Check if employed
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestApplicantPermission@1000000007();
    VAR
      UserSetupManagement@1000000000 : Codeunit 5700;
      ErrStatusPermission@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=You do not have the permission to change the status of your application from %1 to %2. Please contact your administrator.';
    BEGIN
      IF UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '' THEN
        ERROR(ErrStatusPermission, xRec.Status, Status);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestInterviewSchedule@1000000010(DateOfSchedule@1000000000 : Date;TimeOfSchedule@1000000001 : Time);
    VAR
      ErrDateOfInterview@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to schedule an interview earlier than today.';
      InterviewDateTime@1000000003 : DateTime;
    BEGIN
      IF (DateOfSchedule = 0D) OR (TimeOfSchedule = 0T) THEN
        EXIT;
      InterviewDateTime := CREATEDATETIME(DateOfSchedule, TimeOfSchedule);
      IF InterviewDateTime < CURRENTDATETIME THEN
        ERROR(ErrDateOfInterview);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestApplicantQualification@1000000015();
    VAR
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000000 : Record 59019;
    BEGIN
      ApplicantQualifications.ValidateApplicantQualifications("Applicant No.");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE RemoveApplicantOfferLetter@1000000014();
    VAR
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000000 : Record 59019;
    BEGIN
      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE(Type, ApplicantQualifications.Type::"Offer Letter");
      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "Applicant No.");
       IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDFIRST THEN
         ApplicantQualifications.DELETE;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE RemoveApplicantContract@1000000016();
    VAR
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000000 : Record 59019;
    BEGIN
       ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE(Type, ApplicantQualifications.Type::Contract);
       ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "Applicant No.");
       IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDFIRST THEN
         ApplicantQualifications.DELETE;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE RemoveVesselQualificaiton@1000000020();
    VAR
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000000 : Record 59019;
    BEGIN
      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "Applicant No.");
      ApplicantQualifications.SETFILTER("Vessel Code", '<>''''');
       IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDSET THEN
         ApplicantQualifications.DELETEALL;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE RemoveTravelTicketRequest@1000000025();

      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE(Type, ApplicantQualifications.Type::"Travel Ticket");
      IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDFIRST THEN
        ApplicantQualifications.DELETE;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE RemoveVisaRequest@1000000019();

      ApplicantQualifications@1000000000 : Record 59019;

      ApplicantQualifications.SETFILTER(Type, '%1|%2',ApplicantQualifications.Type::"Letter of Guarantee", ApplicantQualifications.Type::Visa);
      IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDSET THEN

    END;

      IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDSET THEN
        ApplicantQualifications.DELETEALL;
