    LOCAL PROCEDURE RemoveContract@1000000017();
    VAR
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000000 : Record 59019;
    BEGIN
      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "Applicant No.");
      ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE(Type,ApplicantQualifications.Type::Contract);
      IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDSET THEN
        ApplicantQualifications.DELETEALL;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GenerateOfferLetter@1000000012();
    VAR
      Qualification@1000000005 : Record 5202;
      JobApplication@1000000004 : Record 59025;
      TempBlob@1000000003 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000006 : Record 59019;
      FileManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 419;
      FilePath@1000000000 : Text;
      ErrOfferLetterQualification@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=Please setup the Offer Letter as qualification in the Qualification List or contact your administrator.';
    BEGIN
       // Generate Offer Letter
      MODIFY;
      JobApplication.SETRANGE("Line No.", "Line No.");
      FilePath := FileManagement.ServerTempFileName('pdf');
      REPORT.SAVEASPDF(REPORT::"Draft Offer Letter", FilePath, JobApplication);
      IF FileManagement.ServerFileExists(FilePath) THEN BEGIN
        TempBlob.INIT;
        FileManagement.BLOBImportFromServerFile(TempBlob,FilePath);
        TempBlob.INSERT;
        TempBlob.CALCFIELDS(Blob);

        Qualification.SETRANGE(Type, Qualification.Type::"Offer Letter");
        IF NOT Qualification.FINDFIRST THEN
          ERROR(ErrOfferLetterQualification);

        Qualification.FINDFIRST;
        IF ApplicantQualifications.GET("Applicant No.", Qualification.Code) THEN
          ApplicantQualifications.DELETE;

        ApplicantQualifications.INIT;
        ApplicantQualifications."Applicant No." := "Applicant No.";
        ApplicantQualifications."Qualification Code" := Qualification.Code;
        ApplicantQualifications."From Date" := "Start Date";
        ApplicantQualifications."To Date" := "End Date";
        ApplicantQualifications."Document No." := FORMAT(Rec.RECORDID);
        ApplicantQualifications."Expiration Date" := "Expiry Date";
        ApplicantQualifications.Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
        ApplicantQualifications.VALIDATE("File Extension", 'pdf');
        ApplicantQualifications."Has Attachment" := TRUE;
        ApplicantQualifications.INSERT;
      END ELSE
        ERROR(Err03);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GenerateContract@1000000030();
    VAR
      Qualification@1000000005 : Record 5202;
      JobApplication@1000000004 : Record 59025;
      TempBlob@1000000003 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000006 : Record 59019;
      FileManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 419;
      FilePath@1000000000 : Text;
    BEGIN
      Qualification.SETRANGE(Type, Qualification.Type::Contract);
      IF Qualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
        MODIFY;
        JobApplication.SETRANGE("Line No.", "Line No.");
        FilePath := FileManagement.ServerTempFileName('pdf');
        REPORT.SAVEASPDF(REPORT::"Applicant Contract", FilePath, JobApplication);
        IF NOT FileManagement.ServerFileExists(FilePath) THEN
          ERROR(Err03);

        TempBlob.INIT;
        FileManagement.BLOBImportFromServerFile(TempBlob,FilePath);
        TempBlob.INSERT;
        TempBlob.CALCFIELDS(Blob);

        RemoveContract;
        TESTFIELD("Sign-On Date");
        TESTFIELD("Sign-Off Date");
        ApplicantQualifications.INIT;
        ApplicantQualifications."Applicant No." := "Applicant No.";
        ApplicantQualifications."Qualification Code" := Qualification.Code;
        ApplicantQualifications."From Date" := "Sign-On Date";
        ApplicantQualifications."To Date" := "Sign-Off Date";
        ApplicantQualifications."Expiration Date" := "Sign-Off Date";
        ApplicantQualifications."Document No." := FORMAT(Rec.RECORDID);
        ApplicantQualifications.Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
        ApplicantQualifications.VALIDATE("File Extension", 'pdf');
        ApplicantQualifications."Has Attachment" := TRUE;
        ApplicantQualifications.INSERT;
      END ELSE
        ERROR(Err02, Qualification.Type::Contract);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GeneratePlaneTicketQualification@1000000026();
    VAR
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000001 : Record 59019;
      Qualification@1000000000 : Record 5202;
    BEGIN
       Qualification.SETRANGE(Type, Qualification.Type::"Travel Ticket");
       IF Qualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          ApplicantQualifications.InsertQualificationFromQualification(Qualification, Rec);
       END ELSE
       ERROR(Err02, Qualification.Type::"Travel Ticket");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GenerateVisaRequest@1000000028();
    VAR
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000001 : Record 59019;
      Qualification@1000000000 : Record 5202;
      ErrNoPlaneTicketQualification@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=Please setup a Qualification for the Type ''Travel Ticket'' or contact your administrator.';
      JobApplication@1000000007 : Record 59025;
      TempBlob@1000000006 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      FileManagement@1000000004 : Codeunit 419;
      FilePath@1000000003 : Text;
    BEGIN
      Qualification.SETRANGE(Type, Qualification.Type::"Letter of Guarantee");
      IF Qualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
        MODIFY;
        JobApplication.SETRANGE("Line No.", "Line No.");
        FilePath := FileManagement.ServerTempFileName('pdf');
        REPORT.SAVEASPDF(REPORT::"Letter of Guarantee", FilePath, JobApplication);
        IF FileManagement.ServerFileExists(FilePath) THEN BEGIN
          TempBlob.INIT;
          FileManagement.BLOBImportFromServerFile(TempBlob,FilePath);
          TempBlob.INSERT;
          TempBlob.CALCFIELDS(Blob);

          IF ApplicantQualifications.GET("Applicant No.", Qualification.Code) THEN
            ApplicantQualifications.DELETE;

          ApplicantQualifications.INIT;
          ApplicantQualifications."Applicant No." := "Applicant No.";
          ApplicantQualifications."Qualification Code" := Qualification.Code;
          ApplicantQualifications."From Date" := TODAY;
          ApplicantQualifications."To Date" := TODAY;
          ApplicantQualifications."Document No." := FORMAT(Rec.RECORDID);
          ApplicantQualifications.Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
          ApplicantQualifications.VALIDATE("File Extension", 'pdf');
          ApplicantQualifications."Has Attachment" := TRUE;
          ApplicantQualifications.INSERT;
        END;
      END ELSE
        ERROR(Err02, Qualification.Type::"Letter of Guarantee");

       CLEAR(Qualification);
       CLEAR(ApplicantQualifications);
       Qualification.SETRANGE(Type, Qualification.Type::Visa);
       IF Qualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          ApplicantQualifications.InsertQualificationFromQualification(Qualification, Rec);
       END ELSE
       ERROR(Err02, Qualification.Type::Visa);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GeneratePPE@1000000023();
    VAR
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000001 : Record 59019;
      Qualification@1000000000 : Record 5202;
    BEGIN
       Qualification.SETRANGE(Type, Qualification.Type::"Personal Protective Equipment");
       IF Qualification.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          ApplicantQualifications.InsertQualificationFromQualification(Qualification, Rec);
       END ELSE
       ERROR(Err02, Qualification.Type::"Personal Protective Equipment");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GenerateVesselQualification@1000000021();
    VAR
      DefaultQualificationValues@1000000000 : Record 59031;
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000001 : Record 59019;
    BEGIN
      DefaultQualificationValues.SetFilterVessel("Vessel Code");
      IF DefaultQualificationValues.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          ApplicantQualifications.InsertQualificationFromDefaultQualifications(Rec,
            DefaultQualificationValues);
        UNTIL DefaultQualificationValues.NEXT = 0;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GeneratePositionQualification@1000000003();
    VAR
      DefaultQualificationValues@1000000000 : Record 59031;
      ApplicantQualifications@1000000001 : Record 59019;
    BEGIN
      // This function is used in the Job Application Event Subscriber
      TESTFIELD("Applicant No.");
      TESTFIELD("Position Code");

      GetApplicant;
      Applicant.TESTFIELD(Status, Applicant.Status::Registered);
      TESTFIELD(Status, Status::"Pending Application");

      // Insert new qualification based on the applied position
      DefaultQualificationValues.SetFilterPosition("Position Code");
      IF DefaultQualificationValues.FINDSET THEN
        REPEAT
          ApplicantQualifications.InsertQualificationFromDefaultQualifications(Rec, DefaultQualificationValues);
        UNTIL DefaultQualificationValues.NEXT = 0;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ClearReceiveDetails@1000000008();
    BEGIN
      CLEAR("Received By User ID");
      CLEAR("Date and Time Received");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ClearInterviewDetails@1000000009();
    BEGIN
      CLEAR("Date of Interview");
      CLEAR("Time of Interview");
      CLEAR(Location);
      CALCFIELDS("Interview Remarks");
      IF "Interview Remarks".HASVALUE THEN
        CLEAR("Interview Remarks");
      "Lock Interview Details" := FALSE;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ClearOfferDetails@1000000011();
    BEGIN
      CLEAR("Oferred By User ID");
      CLEAR("Vessel Code");
      CALCFIELDS(Vessel);
      CLEAR("Currency Code");
      CLEAR("Travel Pay (Day)");
      CLEAR("Offer Salary (Day)");
      CLEAR("Start Date");
      CLEAR("End Date");
      CLEAR("Expiry Date");;
      RemoveApplicantOfferLetter;
      RemoveVesselQualificaiton;
      "Lock Offer Details" := FALSE;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ClearTravelDetails@1000000022();
    BEGIN
      "Lock Travel Details" := FALSE;
      CLEAR("Date of Departure");
      CLEAR("Sign-Off Date");
      CLEAR("Sign-On Date");
      CLEAR("Date of Arrival");
      RemoveTravelTicketRequest;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ClearVisaDetails@1000000029();
    BEGIN
      "Lock Travel Ticket Details" := FALSE;
      CLEAR("Departure Details 1");
      CLEAR("Departure Details 2");
      CLEAR("Departure Details 3");
      CLEAR("Arrival Details 1");
      CLEAR("Arrival Details 2");
      CLEAR("Arrival Details 3");
      RemoveVisaRequest;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetApplicant@1000000000();
    BEGIN
      Applicant.GET("Applicant No.");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetReceivingDetails@1000000005();
    BEGIN
      "Date and Time Received" := CURRENTDATETIME;
      "Received By User ID" := USERID;
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetInterviewRemarks@1000000002(InterviewRemarksTxt@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      OutStr@1000000001 : OutStream;
    BEGIN
      TESTFIELD("Lock Interview Details", FALSE);

      RestrictApplicantModification;

      CALCFIELDS("Interview Remarks");
      IF (NOT "Interview Remarks".HASVALUE) AND (InterviewRemarksTxt = '') THEN
        EXIT;

      IF InterviewRemarksTxt = '' THEN BEGIN
        CLEAR("Interview Remarks");
        MODIFY;
        EXIT;
      END;

      "Interview Remarks".CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      OutStr.WRITETEXT(InterviewRemarksTxt);
      MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetInterviewRemarks@1000000004() : Text;
    VAR
      InterviewRemarksTxt@1000000000 : Text;
      InStr@1000000001 : InStream;
    BEGIN
      InterviewRemarksTxt := '';
      CALCFIELDS("Interview Remarks");
      IF NOT "Interview Remarks".HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT('');

      "Interview Remarks".CREATEINSTREAM(InStr);
      InStr.READTEXT(InterviewRemarksTxt);

      EXIT(InterviewRemarksTxt);
    END;

    BEGIN
    {
      Application Received:
      The employer has received your application. No action has yet been taken, but they acknowledge the submission.

      Under Review:
      Your application is being reviewed by the hiring team. This means they are assessing your qualifications and fit for the role.

      Shortlisted:
      Your application has been selected for further consideration. You may be invited to an interview or additional assessments.

      Interviewing:
      You are in the interview stage of the process. You may be invited for one or more rounds of interviews, which could be conducted in person, via video call, or over the phone.

      Assessment Stage:
      You may be asked to complete an assignment, test, or other types of evaluations to assess your skills.

      Offer Extended:
      The employer has decided to offer you the job. You may receive a formal offer letter or email, which outlines the terms of employment.

      Offer Accepted:
      You have accepted the job offer, and both you and the employer are moving forward with the hiring process.

      Rejected:
      Unfortunately, your application was not successful. This might happen after the review, interview, or assessment stages.

      On Hold:
      The hiring process has been temporarily paused, often due to internal reasons or unforeseen circumstances. You may be contacted later if the role reopens.

      Hired:
      You've been selected and officially hired for the position.
    }
    END.
  }
}

OBJECT Table 59026 Job Qualification
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=06/28/18;
    Time=[ 1:12:53 AM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    OnModify=BEGIN
               GetJobApplicaiton;
               IF JobApplication.Status IN [JobApplication.Status::"Approved By Client", JobApplication.Status::"Cancelled Application"] THEN
                 ERROR(Err03, JobApplication.TABLECAPTION, JobApplication.Status);

               IF NOT (Type IN [Type::Contract, Type::"Offer Letter", Type::Passport,
                   Type::"Seaman Book"]) THEN BEGIN
                 TESTFIELD("From Date");
                 TESTFIELD("To Date");
               END;
             END;

    LookupPageID=Page59026;
    DrillDownPageID=Page59026;
  }
  FIELDS
  {
    { 10  ;   ;Job Application Line No.;Integer    }
    { 15  ;   ;Applicant No.       ;Code20        ;Editable=No }
    { 20  ;   ;Position Code       ;Code10        ;Editable=No }
    { 30  ;   ;Qualification Code  ;Code10        ;OnValidate=VAR
                                                                Qualification@1000000000 : Record 5202;
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                TestJobQualification;
                                                                Qualification.GET("Qualification Code");
                                                                Description := Qualification.Description;
                                                              END;

                                                   Editable=No }
    { 40  ;   ;Description         ;Text50         }
    { 50  ;   ;From Date           ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                TestJobQualification;
                                                                TestType;

                                                                TESTFIELD("From Date");
                                                                IF "From Date" = 0D THEN BEGIN
                                                                  CLEAR("To Date");
                                                                  CLEAR("Expiration Date");
                                                                  EXIT;
                                                                END;

                                                                IF "From Date" > TODAY THEN
                                                                  ERROR( Err01, FIELDNAME("From Date"), TODAY, "From Date");


                                                                IF "From Date" > "To Date" THEN
                                                                  "To Date" := "From Date" + 1;

                                                                "Expiration Date" := "To Date";
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 60  ;   ;To Date             ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                TestJobQualification;
                                                                TestType;

                                                                TESTFIELD("To Date");
                                                                IF "From Date" = 0D THEN BEGIN
                                                                  "From Date" := "To Date" - 1;
                                                                END;

                                                                IF "To Date" < TODAY THEN
                                                                  ERROR(Err02);

                                                                IF "To Date" < "From Date" THEN
                                                                  "From Date" := "To Date" - 1;

                                                                "Expiration Date" := "To Date";
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 70  ;   ;Type                ;Option        ;CaptionML=ENU=Type;
                                                   OptionCaptionML=ENU=" ,Internal,External,Previous Position,Offer Letter,Contract,Passport,Seaman Book";
                                                   OptionString=[ ,Internal,External,Previous Position,Offer Letter,Contract,Passport,Seaman Book] }
    { 90  ;   ;Institution/Company ;Text50        ;CaptionML=ENU=Institution/Company }
    { 100 ;   ;Cost                ;Decimal       ;CaptionML=ENU=Cost;
                                                   AutoFormatType=1 }
    { 110 ;   ;Course Grade        ;Text50        ;CaptionML=ENU=Course Grade }
    { 120 ;   ;Expiration Date     ;Date          ;CaptionML=ENU=Expiration Date }
    { 130 ;   ;Attachment          ;BLOB           }
    { 140 ;   ;Certificate No.     ;Code80         }
  }
  KEYS
  {
    {    ;Job Application Line No.,Applicant No.,Position Code,Qualification Code;
                                                   Clustered=Yes }
  }
  FIELDGROUPS
  {
  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      Err01@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 must not be earlier than %2, currert value is %3.';
      Err02@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to input an expired document.';
      JobApplication@1000000002 : Record 59025;
      UserSetupManagement@1000000003 : Codeunit 5700;

    PROCEDURE SetFilterForApplicant@1000000004();
    VAR
      UserSetupManagement@1000000000 : Codeunit 5700;
    BEGIN
      IF UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '' THEN BEGIN
        FILTERGROUP(2);
        SETRANGE("Applicant No.", UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo);
        FILTERGROUP(0);
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetJobApplicaiton@1000000003();
    BEGIN
      JobApplication.GET("Job Application Line No.");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestJobQualification@1000000000();
    VAR
      JobApplication@1000000000 : Record 59025;
      UserSetupManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 5700;
    BEGIN
      JobApplication.GET("Job Application Line No.");
      IF (UserSetupManagement.GetApplicantNo <> '') AND (JobApplication.Status <> JobApplication.Status::"Pending Application") THEN
        JobApplication.TESTFIELD(Status, JobApplication.Status::"Pending Application");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestType@1000000007();
    BEGIN
      IF Type IN [Type::Contract, Type::"Offer Letter", Type::Passport, Type::"Seaman Book"] THEN
        FIELDERROR(Type);
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetFilterTypePreOnBoardingQualification@1000000001();
    BEGIN
      SETFILTER(Type, '%1|%2|%3|%4', Type::" ", Type::External, Type::Internal, Type::"Previous Position");
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetAttachment@1000000006(Base64TextToBlob@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      RecRef@1000000006 : RecordRef;
      FieldsRef@1000000007 : FieldRef;
      OutStr@1000000004 : OutStream;
      Bytes@1000000003 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN

      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      IF (Base64TextToBlob = '') AND (NOT Attachment.HASVALUE) THEN
        EXIT;

      IF Base64TextToBlob = '' THEN BEGIN
        CLEAR(Attachment);
        MODIFY;
      END;

      Bytes := Convert.FromBase64String(Base64TextToBlob);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream(Bytes);
      Attachment.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      MemoryStream.WriteTo(OutStr);

      MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetAttachment@1000000013() : Text;
    VAR
      BlobToBase64Txt@1000000004 : Text;
      InStr@1000000003 : InStream;
      Bytes@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN
      BlobToBase64Txt := '';
      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      IF NOT Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);

      Attachment.CREATEINSTREAM(InStr);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream();
      COPYSTREAM(MemoryStream, InStr);
      Bytes := MemoryStream.GetBuffer();
      BlobToBase64Txt := Convert.ToBase64String(Bytes);
      EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

               TESTFIELD(Company);
               TESTFIELD(Position);

             END;

OBJECT Table 59028 Applicant Job History
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=06/27/18;
    Time=[ 1:43:15 AM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    OnInsert=BEGIN
               TESTFIELD("Applicant No.");
               TESTFIELD(Rank);
               TESTFIELD("Ship Name");
               TESTFIELD("Flag Code");
               TESTFIELD(Type);
               SetJobHistoryDates(0);
               SetJobHistoryDuration;
             END;

    OnModify=BEGIN
               TESTFIELD("Applicant No.");
               TESTFIELD(Rank);
               TESTFIELD("Ship Name");
               TESTFIELD("Flag Code");
               TESTFIELD(Type);
               SetJobHistoryDates(0);
               SetJobHistoryDuration;
             END;

  }
  FIELDS
  {
    { 10  ;   ;Line No.            ;Integer        }
    { 20  ;   ;Applicant No.       ;Code20        ;TableRelation=Applicant }
    { 30  ;   ;Rank                ;Code80         }
    { 40  ;   ;Ship Name           ;Code100        }
    { 50  ;   ;Flag Code           ;Code10        ;TableRelation=Country/Region }
    { 60  ;   ;Type                ;Code50         }
    { 70  ;   ;ENG Type/Auxiliary  ;Code50         }
    { 80  ;   ;GRT                 ;Code30         }
    { 90  ;   ;BHP                 ;Code20         }
    { 100 ;   ;Trading Area / AOP  ;Code80        ;CaptionML=ENU=Trading Area / Area of Operation }
    { 110 ;   ;Sign On             ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                // TODO validate the date
                                                                // Sign-On date should not be greater than today.
                                                                IF "Sign On" <> xRec."Sign On" THEN
                                                                  SetJobHistoryDates(FIELDNO("Sign On"));
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 120 ;   ;Sign Off            ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                // TODO validate the date
                                                                // Sign-Off date should not be greater than today.
                                                                IF  "Sign Off" <> xRec."Sign Off" THEN
                                                                  SetJobHistoryDates(FIELDNO("Sign Off"));
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 130 ;   ;Year                ;Integer       ;Editable=No }
    { 140 ;   ;Month               ;Integer       ;Editable=No }
    { 150 ;   ;Day                 ;Integer       ;Editable=No }
  }
  KEYS
  {
    {    ;Applicant No.,Line No.                  ;Clustered=Yes }
  }
  FIELDGROUPS
  {
  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      Err01@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=The %1 date must be earlier than %2.';
      Err02@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=The %1 date cannot be later than the %2 date.';
      Err03@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU="The %1 date must be earlier than the %2 date. "';
      Err04@1000000003 : TextConst 'ENU=The %1 date cannot be earlier than the %2 date.';
      Err05@1000000004 : TextConst 'ENU=The %1 date must be later than the %2 date.';
      Err06@1000000005 : TextConst 'ENU=Please select a valid option.';

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetJobHistoryDuration@1000000027();
    VAR
      Err01@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 must not be later than %2. Current value is %3.';
    BEGIN
      // Set Job History / Sea Time
      IF "Sign On" > "Sign Off" THEN
        ERROR(Err01, FIELDNAME("Sign On"), FIELDNAME("Sign Off"), "Sign On");

      Year := GetYearOfExperience;
      Month := GetMonthOfExperience;
      Day := GetDayOfExperience;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetYearOfExperience@1000000004() : Integer;
    VAR
      TempYear@1000000000 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      // Calcualte the Year of Experience
      TempYear := 0;
      IF ("Sign On" = 0D ) AND ("Sign Off" = 0D) THEN
       EXIT(TempYear);

      TempYear := DATE2DMY("Sign Off", 3) - DATE2DMY("Sign On", 3);
      IF TempYear <= 0 THEN
        EXIT(0);

      IF CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1Y>', TempYear),"Sign On") > "Sign Off" THEN
        TempYear -= 1;

      EXIT(TempYear);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetMonthOfExperience@1000000003() : Integer;
    VAR
      TempMonth@1000000000 : Integer;
      TempYear@1000000002 : Integer;
      TempDate@1000000001 : Date;
    BEGIN
      // Calculate the Month of Experience
      TempMonth := 0;

      IF ("Sign On" = 0D) AND ("Sign Off" = 0D) THEN
        EXIT(TempMonth);

      TempMonth := DATE2DMY("Sign Off", 2) - DATE2DMY("Sign On", 2);

      IF TempMonth = 0 THEN
        EXIT(0);

      IF TempMonth < 0 THEN
        TempMonth += 12;

      TempDate := "Sign On";
      TempDate := CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1Y>', GetYearOfExperience), "Sign On");
      TempDate := CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1M>', TempMonth), TempDate);

      IF TempDate > "Sign Off" THEN
        TempMonth -= 1;

      EXIT(TempMonth);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetDayOfExperience@1000000014() : Integer;
    VAR
      TempDay@1000000000 : Integer;
      TempDate@1000000001 : Date;
    BEGIN
      // Calculate the Day of Experience
      TempDay := 0;

      IF ("Sign On" = 0D) AND ("Sign Off" = 0D) THEN
        EXIT(TempDay);

      TempDate := "Sign On";
      TempDate := CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1Y>', GetYearOfExperience), "Sign On");
      TempDate := CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1M>', GetMonthOfExperience), TempDate);

      TempDay := "Sign Off" - TempDate;

      IF TempDay <= 0 THEN
        EXIT(0);

      TempDate := CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1D>', TempDay), "Sign On");
      IF TempDate > "Sign Off" THEN
        TempDay -= 1;

      EXIT(TempDay);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetJobHistoryDates@1000000000(RecFieldNo@1000000000 : Integer);
    BEGIN
      CASE RecFieldNo OF
        FIELDNO("Sign On"):
          BEGIN

            // insert custom date if blank.

            // validate sign on date.
            IF ("Sign On" > TODAY) OR ("Sign On" = TODAY) THEN
                ERROR(Err01, FIELDCAPTION("Sign On"), TODAY);
            IF "Sign Off" <> 0D THEN BEGIN
              IF "Sign On" > "Sign Off" THEN
                ERROR(Err02, FIELDCAPTION("Sign On"), FIELDCAPTION("Sign Off"));
              IF "Sign On" = "Sign Off" THEN
                ERROR(Err03, FIELDCAPTION("Sign On"),  FIELDCAPTION("Sign Off"))
            END;
          END;
        FIELDNO("Sign Off"):
          BEGIN

            // insert custom date if blank.

            // validate sign off date.
            IF ("Sign Off" > TODAY) OR ("Sign Off" = TODAY) THEN
                ERROR(Err01, FIELDCAPTION("Sign Off"), TODAY);
            IF "Sign On" <> 0D THEN BEGIN
              IF "Sign Off" < "Sign On" THEN
                ERROR(Err04, FIELDCAPTION("Sign Off"),  FIELDCAPTION("Sign On"));
              IF "Sign Off" = "Sign On" THEN
                ERROR(Err05, FIELDCAPTION("Sign Off"), FIELDCAPTION("Sign On"));
            END;

          END;
        ELSE BEGIN
          TESTFIELD("Sign On");
          TESTFIELD("Sign Off");
        END;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetSumSeaTime@1000000001(VAR ApplicantNo@1000000000 : Code[10];Option@1000000001 : 'Year,Month,Day') : Integer;
    VAR
      ApplicantJobHistory@1000000005 : Record 59028;
    BEGIN
      ApplicantJobHistory.RESET;
      ApplicantJobHistory.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", ApplicantNo);
      IF ApplicantJobHistory.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        CASE Option OF
        Option::Year:
          BEGIN
            ApplicantJobHistory.CALCSUMS(Year);
            EXIT(ApplicantJobHistory.Year);
          END;
        Option::Month:
          BEGIN
            ApplicantJobHistory.CALCSUMS(Month);
            EXIT(ApplicantJobHistory.Month);
          END;
        Option::Day:
          BEGIN
            ApplicantJobHistory.CALCSUMS(Day);
            EXIT(ApplicantJobHistory.Day);
          END;
        ELSE
          ERROR(Err06);
        END;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetTotalSeaTime@1000000002(ApplicantNo@1000000000 : Code[20];Option@1000000002 : 'Year,Month,Day') : Integer;
    VAR
      ApplicantJobHistory@1000000001 : Record 59028;
      VarSumYear@1000000003 : Integer;
      VarSumMonth@1000000004 : Integer;
      VarSumDay@1000000005 : Integer;
      VarTotalMonth@1000000007 : Integer;
      VarTotalYear@1000000009 : Integer;
      TotalYear@1000000006 : Integer;
      TotalDay@1000000008 : Integer;
      TotalMonth@1000000010 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      ApplicantJobHistory.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", ApplicantNo);
      IF ApplicantJobHistory.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        // get sum of year, month and day.
        VarSumYear := GetSumSeaTime(ApplicantNo, 0);
        VarSumMonth := GetSumSeaTime(ApplicantNo, 1);
        VarSumDay := GetSumSeaTime(ApplicantNo, 2);

        EVALUATE(VarTotalMonth, FORMAT((VarSumDay / 30),0,'<Integer>'));
        EVALUATE(VarTotalYear, FORMAT(((VarSumMonth + VarTotalMonth) / 12),0,'<Integer>'));

        CASE Option OF
          Option::Year:
            BEGIN
              EXIT(VarSumYear + VarTotalYear);
            END;
          Option::Month:
            BEGIN
              EXIT(ROUND(((((VarSumMonth + VarTotalMonth) / 12) - VarTotalYear) * 12),1,'='));
            END;
          Option::Day:
            BEGIN
              EXIT(ROUND((((VarSumDay / 30) - VarTotalMonth) * 30),1,'='));
            END;
          ELSE
            ERROR(Err06);
        END;
      END;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {

  }
  PROPERTIES

  }
  FIELDS
  {
    { 10  ;   ;Line No.            ;Integer       ;AutoIncrement=Yes;
                                                   Editable=No }
    { 20  ;   ;Table ID            ;Integer       ;TableRelation=AllObjWithCaption."Object ID" WHERE (Object Type=CONST(Table));
                                                   NotBlank=Yes }
    { 30  ;   ;No.                 ;Code20        ;TableRelation=IF (Table ID=CONST(5200)) Employee.No.
                                                                 ELSE IF (Table ID=CONST(59010)) Applicant.No.;
                                                   NotBlank=Yes }
    { 35  ;   ;Date                ;Date           }
    { 40  ;   ;Diagnosis           ;Code250        }
    { 50  ;   ;Remarks             ;BLOB           }
    { 60  ;   ;Attachment          ;BLOB           }
    { 61  ;   ;File Extension      ;Text30        ;OnValidate=VAR
                                                                FileExtensionText@1000000001 : TextConst '@@@={Locked};ENU=pdf,jpeg,png,gif,svg';
                                                                ErrFileExtension@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re passing an invalid file extension.';
                                                              BEGIN
                                                                 IF STRPOS(FileExtensionText, "File Extension") = 0 THEN
                                                                  ERROR(ErrFileExtension);
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 62  ;   ;Has Attachment      ;Boolean       ;Editable=No }
    { 70  ;   ;User ID             ;Code250       ;TableRelation="User Setup";
                                                   Editable=No }

  CODE

    PROCEDURE SetRemarks@1000000003(Base64TextToBlob@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      RecRef@1000000006 : RecordRef;
      FieldsRef@1000000007 : FieldRef;
      OutStr@1000000004 : OutStream;
      Bytes@1000000003 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
      MimeType@1000000005 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS(Remarks);
      IF (Base64TextToBlob = '') AND (NOT Remarks.HASVALUE) THEN
        EXIT;

      IF Base64TextToBlob = '' THEN BEGIN
        CLEAR(Remarks);
        MODIFY;
      END;

      Remarks.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      OutStr.WRITE(Base64TextToBlob);
      IF ("Line No." <> 0) THEN
        MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetRemarks@1000000002() : Text;
    VAR
      BlobToBase64Txt@1000000004 : Text;
      InStr@1000000003 : InStream;
      Bytes@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN
      BlobToBase64Txt := '';
      CALCFIELDS(Remarks);
      IF NOT Remarks.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);

      BlobToBase64Txt := ReadBLOB(FIELDNO(Remarks));

      EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetAttachment@1000000006(Base64TextToBlob@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      RecRef@1000000006 : RecordRef;
      FieldsRef@1000000007 : FieldRef;
      OutStr@1000000004 : OutStream;
      Bytes@1000000003 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
      MimeType@1000000005 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
      IF (Base64TextToBlob = '') AND (NOT Attachment.HASVALUE) THEN
        EXIT;

      IF Base64TextToBlob = '' THEN BEGIN
        CLEAR(Attachment);
        CLEAR("File Extension");
        CLEAR("Has Attachment");
        MODIFY;
      END;

      Bytes := Convert.FromBase64String(Base64TextToBlob);
      MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream(Bytes);
      Attachment.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      MemoryStream.WriteTo(OutStr);
       "Has Attachment" := TRUE;
      IF ("Line No." <> 0) THEN
        MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetAttachment@1000000013() : Text;
    VAR
      BlobToBase64Txt@1000000004 : Text;
      InStr@1000000003 : InStream;
      Bytes@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN
       BlobToBase64Txt := '';
       CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
       IF NOT Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);

       Attachment.CREATEINSTREAM(InStr);
       MemoryStream := MemoryStream.MemoryStream();
       COPYSTREAM(MemoryStream, InStr);
       Bytes := MemoryStream.GetBuffer();
       BlobToBase64Txt := Convert.ToBase64String(Bytes);
       EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);
    END;

    PROCEDURE ImportAttachment@1000000022();
    VAR
      ErrChangeAttachment@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=Do you want to change the attachment?';
      TempBlob@1000000002 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      FileManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 419;
      ImportTxt@1000000006 : TextConst 'ENU=Select a file to import';
      FileFilterTxt@1000000005 : TextConst '@@@=Do not translate the file extensions (e.g. .xml, .txt, .csv, etc);ENU="PDF Files(*.pdf)|*.pdf|Image Files(*.jpeg;*.png;*.gif;*.svg)|*.jpeg;*.png;*.gif;*.svg"';
      FileFilterExtensionTxt@1000000004 : TextConst '@@@={Locked};ENU=pdf,jpeg,png,gif,svg';
      FilePath@1000000007 : Text;
      FileExtension@1000000003 : Text;
    BEGIN
       CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
       IF Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        IF NOT CONFIRM(ErrChangeAttachment,FALSE) THEN
          EXIT;
        FilePath := FileManagement.BLOBImportWithFilter(TempBlob, ImportTxt, '',FileFilterTxt, FileFilterExtensionTxt);
       IF FilePath = '' THEN
        EXIT;
       TempBlob.INSERT;

       FileExtension := FileManagement.GetExtension(FilePath);
       TempBlob.CALCFIELDS(Blob);

       VALIDATE("File Extension", FileExtension);
       TESTFIELD("File Extension");

       Attachment := TempBlob.Blob;
       "Has Attachment" := TRUE;
       MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE ExportAttachment@5(UseDialog@1002 : Boolean) : Text;
    VAR
      TempBlob@1000 : TEMPORARY Record 99008535;
      FileMgt@1001 : Codeunit 419;
      OutStream@1004 : OutStream;
      FileName@1003 : Text;
    BEGIN
       CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
       IF NOT Attachment.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT;

       CALCFIELDS(Diagnosis);
       FileName := Diagnosis + '.' + "File Extension";

       CALCFIELDS(Attachment);
       TempBlob.INIT;
       TempBlob.Blob := Attachment;
       TempBlob.INSERT;
       TempBlob.Blob.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStream);

       EXIT(FileMgt.BLOBExport(TempBlob,FileName,UseDialog));
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ReadBLOB@3(FieldNo@1002 : Integer) : Text;
    VAR
      TypeHelper@1000000001 : Codeunit 10;
      RecordRef@1001 : RecordRef;
      FieldRef@1003 : FieldRef;
      Environment@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=4.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Environment";
    BEGIN
      RecordRef.GETTABLE(Rec);
      FieldRef := RecordRef.FIELD(FieldNo);
      EXIT(TypeHelper.ReadTextBlob(FieldRef,Environment.NewLine));
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

OBJECT Table 59033 Interview Schedule
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=06/26/18;
    Time=[ 1:03:06 AM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    Permissions=TableData 1511=i;
    OnInsert=BEGIN
               TestJobApplicationStatusUnderReview;
               TESTFIELD("Date of Schedule");
               TESTFIELD("Time of Schedule");
               TestSchedules;
               TESTFIELD(Subject);

               IF JobApplication.Status = JobApplication.Status::"Under Review" THEN BEGIN
                 JobApplication.VALIDATE(Status, JobApplication.Status::Interviewing);
                 JobApplication.MODIFY(TRUE);
               END;

               SendEmailInterview;
             END;

    OnModify=BEGIN
               TestJobApplicationStatusUnderReview;
               TESTFIELD("Date of Schedule");
               TESTFIELD("Time of Schedule");
               TESTFIELD(Subject);

               IF ("Date of Schedule" <> xRec."Date of Schedule") OR
                   ("Time of Schedule" <> xRec."Time of Schedule") THEN BEGIN
                 TestSchedules;
                 SendEmailInterview;
               END;
             END;

  }
  FIELDS
  {
    { 10  ;   ;Line No.            ;Integer       ;Editable=No }
    { 15  ;   ;Job Application No. ;Integer       ;NotBlank=Yes }
    { 20  ;   ;Applicant No.       ;Code20        ;TableRelation=Applicant;
                                                   NotBlank=No }
    { 30  ;   ;Date of Schedule    ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                // IF "Date of Schedule"
                                                                // IF "Date of Schedule" < TODAY THEN
                                                                //  ERROR(Err01, TODAY, "Date of Schedule");
                                                              END;

                                                   CaptionML=ENU=Date }
    { 40  ;   ;Time of Schedule    ;Time          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                // IF "Time of Schedule" < TIME THEN
                                                                //  ERROR(Err01, TIME, "Time of Schedule");
                                                              END;

                                                   CaptionML=ENU=Time }
    { 50  ;   ;Subject             ;Text250        }
    { 60  ;   ;Location            ;Text250        }
    { 70  ;   ;Remarks             ;BLOB           }
    { 80  ;   ;Status              ;Option        ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                IF Status = Status::Failed THEN BEGIN
                                                                  JobApplication.GET("Job Application No.");
                                                                  JobApplication.VALIDATE(Status, JobApplication.Status::"Not Approved By Client");
                                                                  JobApplication.MODIFY(TRUE);
                                                                END;
                                                              END;

                                                   OptionCaptionML=ENU=" ,Passed,Failed";
                                                   OptionString=[ ,Passed,Failed] }
  }
  KEYS
  {
    {    ;Job Application No.,Applicant No.,Line No.;
                                                   Clustered=Yes }
  }
  FIELDGROUPS
  {
  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      JobApplication@1000000000 : Record 59025;
      TempScheduleDateTime@1000000001 : DateTime;
      Err01@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=The schedule of the interview must be earlier than %1. Current value is %2.';

    PROCEDURE SetInterviewRemarks@1000000002(InterviewRemarksTxt@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      OutStr@1000000001 : OutStream;
    BEGIN
      CALCFIELDS(Remarks);
      IF (NOT Remarks.HASVALUE) AND (InterviewRemarksTxt = '') THEN
        EXIT;

      IF InterviewRemarksTxt = '' THEN BEGIN
        CLEAR(Remarks);
        MODIFY;
        EXIT;
      END;

      Remarks.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      OutStr.WRITETEXT(InterviewRemarksTxt);
      IF ("Line No." <> 0) AND ("Applicant No." <> '') AND ("Job Application No." <> 0) THEN
        MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetInterviewRemarks@1000000004() : Text;
    VAR
      InterviewRemarksTxt@1000000000 : Text;
      InStr@1000000001 : InStream;
    BEGIN
      InterviewRemarksTxt := '';
      CALCFIELDS(Remarks);
      IF NOT Remarks.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT('');

      Remarks.CREATEINSTREAM(InStr);
      InStr.READTEXT(InterviewRemarksTxt);

      EXIT(InterviewRemarksTxt);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetJobApplication@1000000005();
    BEGIN
      JobApplication.GET("Job Application No.");
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestJobApplicationStatusUnderReview@1000000001();
    BEGIN
      GetJobApplication;
      IF NOT (JobApplication.Status IN [JobApplication.Status::"Under Review",
          JobApplication.Status::Interviewing]) THEN
        JobApplication.FIELDERROR(Status);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE TestSchedules@1000000006();
    BEGIN
      IF CREATEDATETIME("Date of Schedule", "Time of Schedule") < CURRENTDATETIME THEN
        ERROR(Err01, CURRENTDATETIME, CREATEDATETIME("Date of Schedule", "Time of Schedule"));
    END;

    PROCEDURE SendEmailInterview@1000000018();
    VAR
      NotificationEntry@1000000001 : Record 1511;
      Applicant@1000000000 : Record 59010;
      UserSetup@1000000002 : Record 91;
    BEGIN
      IF Applicant.GET("Applicant No.") THEN BEGIN
        UserSetup.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", Applicant."No.");
        IF UserSetup.FINDFIRST THEN
          NotificationEntry.CreateNew2(NotificationEntry.Type::"N-JAppIntv",
            UserSetup."User ID",Rec,0,'','','','',Subject);
      END;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

OBJECT Table 59034 Employee Sea Service Record
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=06/26/18;
    Time=12:01:37 AM;
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    OnInsert=BEGIN
               TESTFIELD("Employee No.");
               TESTFIELD(Rank);
               TESTFIELD("Ship Name");
               TESTFIELD("Flag Code");
               TESTFIELD(Type);
               SetSeaServiceDates(0);
               SetJobHistoryDuration;
             END;

    OnModify=BEGIN
               TESTFIELD("Employee No.");
               TESTFIELD(Rank);
               TESTFIELD("Ship Name");
               TESTFIELD("Flag Code");
               TESTFIELD(Type);
               SetSeaServiceDates(0);
               SetJobHistoryDuration;
             END;

    OnDelete=VAR
               EmployeeSeaServiceRecord@1000000000 : Record 59034;
               Employee@1000000001 : Record 5200;
             BEGIN
               EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.SETRANGE("Employee No.", "Employee No.");
               EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.SETFILTER("Line No.",'<>%1', "Line No.");
               IF NOT EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.FINDFIRST THEN
                 ERROR(Err06, Employee.TABLECAPTION, "Employee No.");
             END;

  }
  FIELDS
  {
    { 10  ;   ;Line No.            ;Integer        }
    { 20  ;   ;Employee No.        ;Code20        ;TableRelation=Employee }
    { 30  ;   ;Rank                ;Code80         }
    { 40  ;   ;Ship Name           ;Code100        }
    { 50  ;   ;Flag Code           ;Code10        ;TableRelation=Country/Region }
    { 60  ;   ;Type                ;Code50         }
    { 70  ;   ;ENG Type/Auxiliary  ;Code50         }
    { 80  ;   ;GRT                 ;Code30         }
    { 90  ;   ;BHP                 ;Code20         }
    { 100 ;   ;Trading Area / AOP  ;Code80        ;CaptionML=ENU=Trading Area / Area of Operation }
    { 110 ;   ;Sign On             ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                IF "Sign On" <> xRec."Sign On" THEN
                                                                  SetSeaServiceDates(FIELDNO("Sign On"));
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 120 ;   ;Sign Off            ;Date          ;OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                IF  "Sign Off" <> xRec."Sign Off" THEN
                                                                  SetSeaServiceDates(FIELDNO("Sign Off"));
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 130 ;   ;Year                ;Integer       ;Editable=No }
    { 140 ;   ;Month               ;Integer       ;Editable=No }
    { 150 ;   ;Day                 ;Integer       ;Editable=No }
  }
  KEYS
  {
    {    ;Employee No.,Line No.                   ;Clustered=Yes }
  }
  FIELDGROUPS
  {
  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      Err01@1000000004 : TextConst 'ENU=The %1 date must be earlier than %2.';
      Err02@1000000003 : TextConst 'ENU=The %1 date cannot be later than the %2 date.';
      Err03@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU="The %1 date must be earlier than the %2 date. "';
      Err04@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=The %1 date cannot be earlier than the %2 date.';
      Err05@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=The %1 date must be later than the %2 date.';
      Err06@1000000005 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 %2 must have at least one (1) Sea Service Record.';

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetJobHistoryDuration@1000000027();
    VAR
      Err01@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=%1 must not be later than %2. Current value is %3.';
    BEGIN
      // Set Job History / Sea Time
      IF "Sign On" > "Sign Off" THEN
        ERROR(Err01, FIELDNAME("Sign On"), FIELDNAME("Sign Off"), "Sign On");

      Year := GetYearOfExperience;
      Month := GetMonthOfExperience;
      Day := GetDayOfExperience;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetYearOfExperience@1000000004() : Integer;
    VAR
      TempYear@1000000000 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      // Calcualte the Year of Experience
      TempYear := 0;
      IF ("Sign On" = 0D ) AND ("Sign Off" = 0D) THEN
       EXIT(TempYear);

      TempYear := DATE2DMY("Sign Off", 3) - DATE2DMY("Sign On", 3);
      IF TempYear <= 0 THEN
        EXIT(0);

      IF CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1Y>', TempYear),"Sign On") > "Sign Off" THEN
        TempYear -= 1;

      EXIT(TempYear);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetMonthOfExperience@1000000003() : Integer;
    VAR
      TempMonth@1000000000 : Integer;
      TempYear@1000000002 : Integer;
      TempDate@1000000001 : Date;
    BEGIN
      // Calculate the Month of Experience
      TempMonth := 0;

      IF ("Sign On" = 0D) AND ("Sign Off" = 0D) THEN
        EXIT(TempMonth);

      TempMonth := DATE2DMY("Sign Off", 2) - DATE2DMY("Sign On", 2);

      IF TempMonth = 0 THEN
        EXIT(0);

      IF TempMonth < 0 THEN
        TempMonth += 12;

      TempDate := "Sign On";
      TempDate := CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1Y>', GetYearOfExperience), "Sign On");
      TempDate := CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1M>', TempMonth), TempDate);

      IF TempDate > "Sign Off" THEN
        TempMonth -= 1;

      EXIT(TempMonth);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE GetDayOfExperience@1000000014() : Integer;
    VAR
      TempDay@1000000000 : Integer;
      TempDate@1000000001 : Date;
    BEGIN
      // Calculate the Day of Experience
      TempDay := 0;

      IF ("Sign On" = 0D) AND ("Sign Off" = 0D) THEN
        EXIT(TempDay);

      TempDate := "Sign On";
      TempDate := CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1Y>', GetYearOfExperience), "Sign On");
      TempDate := CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1M>', GetMonthOfExperience), TempDate);

      TempDay := "Sign Off" - TempDate;

      IF TempDay <= 0 THEN
        EXIT(0);

      TempDate := CALCDATE(STRSUBSTNO('<%1D>', TempDay), "Sign On");
      IF TempDate > "Sign Off" THEN
        TempDay -= 1;

      EXIT(TempDay);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE SetSeaServiceDates@1000000000(RecFieldNo@1000000000 : Integer);
    BEGIN
      CASE RecFieldNo OF
        FIELDNO("Sign On"):
          BEGIN

            // insert custom date if blank.

            // validate sign on date.
            IF ("Sign On" > TODAY) OR ("Sign On" = TODAY) THEN
                ERROR(Err01, FIELDCAPTION("Sign On"), TODAY);
            IF "Sign Off" <> 0D THEN BEGIN
              IF "Sign On" > "Sign Off" THEN
                ERROR(Err02, FIELDCAPTION("Sign On"), FIELDCAPTION("Sign Off"));
              IF "Sign On" = "Sign Off" THEN
                ERROR(Err03, FIELDCAPTION("Sign On"),  FIELDCAPTION("Sign Off"))
            END;
          END;
        FIELDNO("Sign Off"):
          BEGIN

            // insert custom date if blank.

            // validate sign off date.
            IF ("Sign Off" > TODAY) OR ("Sign Off" = TODAY) THEN
                ERROR(Err01, FIELDCAPTION("Sign Off"), TODAY);
            IF "Sign On" <> 0D THEN BEGIN
              IF "Sign Off" < "Sign On" THEN
                ERROR(Err04, FIELDCAPTION("Sign Off"),  FIELDCAPTION("Sign On"));
              IF "Sign Off" = "Sign On" THEN
                ERROR(Err05, FIELDCAPTION("Sign Off"), FIELDCAPTION("Sign On"));
            END;

          END;
        ELSE BEGIN
          TESTFIELD("Sign On");
          TESTFIELD("Sign Off");
        END;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetSumSeaTime@1000000001(VAR EmployeeNo@1000000000 : Code[10];Option@1000000001 : 'Year,Month,Day') : Integer;
    VAR
      EmployeeSeaServiceRecord@1000000002 : Record 59034;
    BEGIN
      EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.RESET;
      EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.SETRANGE("Employee No.", EmployeeNo);
      IF EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        CASE Option OF
        Option::Year:
          BEGIN
            EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.CALCSUMS(Year);
            EXIT(EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.Year);
          END;
        Option::Month:
          BEGIN
            EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.CALCSUMS(Month);
            EXIT(EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.Month);
          END;
        Option::Day:
          BEGIN
            EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.CALCSUMS(Day);
            EXIT(EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.Day);
          END;
        ELSE
          ERROR(Err06);
        END;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetTotalSeaTime@1000000002(VAR EmployeeNo@1000000000 : Code[10];Option@1000000002 : 'Year,Month,Day') : Integer;
    VAR
      EmployeeSeaServiceRecord@1000000001 : Record 59034;
      VarSumYear@1000000003 : Integer;
      VarSumMonth@1000000004 : Integer;
      VarSumDay@1000000005 : Integer;
      VarTotalMonth@1000000007 : Integer;
      VarTotalYear@1000000009 : Integer;
      TotalYear@1000000006 : Integer;
      TotalDay@1000000008 : Integer;
      TotalMonth@1000000010 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.RESET;
      EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.SETRANGE("Employee No.", EmployeeNo);
      IF EmployeeSeaServiceRecord.FINDSET THEN BEGIN

        // get sum of year, month and day.
        VarSumYear := GetSumSeaTime(EmployeeNo, 0);
        VarSumMonth := GetSumSeaTime(EmployeeNo, 1);
        VarSumDay := GetSumSeaTime(EmployeeNo, 2);

        EVALUATE(VarTotalMonth, FORMAT((VarSumDay / 30),0,'<Integer>'));
        EVALUATE(VarTotalYear, FORMAT(((VarSumMonth + VarTotalMonth) / 12),0,'<Integer>'));

        CASE Option OF
          Option::Year:
            BEGIN
              EXIT(VarSumYear + VarTotalYear);
            END;
          Option::Month:
            BEGIN
              EXIT(ROUND(((((VarSumMonth + VarTotalMonth) / 12) - VarTotalYear) * 12),1,'='));
            END;
          Option::Day:
            BEGIN
              EXIT(ROUND((((VarSumDay / 30) - VarTotalMonth) * 30),1,'='));
            END;
          ELSE
            ERROR(Err06);
        END;
      END;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

OBJECT Table 59303 Generic Note
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=06/27/18;
    Time=[ 8:30:00 AM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    OnInsert=BEGIN
               Created := CURRENTDATETIME;
               "User ID" := USERID;
             END;

    OnModify=BEGIN
               IF "User ID" <> USERID THEN
                 ERROR(Err02, "Line No.");

               Modified := CURRENTDATETIME;
             END;

    OnDelete=BEGIN
               IF "User ID" <> USERID THEN
                 ERROR(Err01, "Line No.");
             END;

  }
  FIELDS
  {
    { 10  ;   ;Line No.            ;Integer       ;AutoIncrement=Yes;
                                                   Editable=No }
    { 20  ;   ;Table ID            ;Integer       ;TableRelation=AllObjWithCaption."Object ID" WHERE (Object Type=CONST(Table));
                                                   OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                IF xRec."Table ID" <> 0 THEN
                                                                  TESTFIELD("Table ID", xRec."Table ID");
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 30  ;   ;No.                 ;Code250       ;TableRelation=IF (Table ID=CONST(59025)) "Job Application";
                                                   OnValidate=BEGIN
                                                                IF xRec."No." <> '' THEN
                                                                  TESTFIELD("No.", xRec."No.");
                                                              END;
                                                               }
    { 40  ;   ;Note                ;BLOB           }
    { 50  ;   ;Created             ;DateTime      ;Editable=No }
    { 55  ;   ;Modified            ;DateTime      ;Editable=No }
    { 60  ;   ;User ID             ;Code250       ;Editable=No }
    { 70  ;   ;To User ID          ;Code250        }
  }
  KEYS
  {
    {    ;Line No.                                ;Clustered=Yes }
  }
  FIELDGROUPS
  {
  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      Err01@1000000000 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to delete the Note %1.';
      Err02@1000000001 : TextConst 'ENU=You''re not allowed to modify the Note %1.';

    PROCEDURE SetNote@1000000006(Base64TextToBlob@1000000000 : Text);
    VAR
      RecRef@1000000006 : RecordRef;
      FieldsRef@1000000007 : FieldRef;
      OutStr@1000000004 : OutStream;
      Bytes@1000000003 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
      MimeType@1000000005 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
    BEGIN
      IF "User ID" <> USERID THEN
        ERROR(Err01, "Line No.");

      CALCFIELDS(Note);
      IF (Base64TextToBlob = '') AND (NOT Note.HASVALUE) THEN
        EXIT;

      IF Base64TextToBlob = '' THEN BEGIN
        CLEAR(Note);
        MODIFY;
      END;

      Note.CREATEOUTSTREAM(OutStr);
      OutStr.WRITE(Base64TextToBlob);
      IF ("Line No." <> 0) AND ("Table ID" <> 0) AND ("No." <> '') THEN
        MODIFY;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetNote@1000000013() : Text;
    VAR
      BlobToBase64Txt@1000000004 : Text;
      InStr@1000000003 : InStream;
      Bytes@1000000002 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Array";
      Convert@1000000001 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Convert";
      MemoryStream@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=2.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.IO.MemoryStream";
    BEGIN
      BlobToBase64Txt := '';
      CALCFIELDS(Note);
      IF NOT Note.HASVALUE THEN
        EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);

      BlobToBase64Txt := ReadBLOB(FIELDNO(Note));

      EXIT(BlobToBase64Txt);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ReadBLOB@3(FieldNo@1002 : Integer) : Text;
    VAR
      TypeHelper@1000000001 : Codeunit 10;
      RecordRef@1001 : RecordRef;
      FieldRef@1003 : FieldRef;
      Environment@1000000000 : DotNet "'mscorlib, Version=4.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089'.System.Environment";
    BEGIN
      RecordRef.GETTABLE(Rec);
      FieldRef := RecordRef.FIELD(FieldNo);
      EXIT(TypeHelper.ReadTextBlob(FieldRef,Environment.NewLine));
    END;

    PROCEDURE SetDefaultFilter@1000000000();
    BEGIN
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

OBJECT Table 59310 Crew Certificates
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=06/28/18;
    Time=[ 2:11:25 AM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
  }
  FIELDS
  {
    { 1   ;   ;Certificate Code    ;Code10         }
    { 2   ;   ;Certificate Description;Text30      }
    { 3   ;   ;Certificate No      ;Text30         }
    { 4   ;   ;Issue Date          ;Date           }
    { 5   ;   ;Expiry Date         ;Date           }
  }
  KEYS
  {
    {    ;Certificate Code                        ;Clustered=Yes }
  }
  FIELDGROUPS
  {
  }
  CODE

  DATASET
  {
    { 1000000000;;DataItem;                  ;
               DataItemTable=Table59025;
               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  RowCount := 0;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=Line No.,Applicant No.,Status }

    { 1000000075;1;Column;JobApplicationLineNo;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Line No." }

    { 1000000001;1;Column;ApplicantNo        ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Applicant No." }

               SourceExpr="Job Application".Description }

    { 1000000004;1;DataItem;                 ;
               DataItemTable=Table59010;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(No.)
                                 ORDER(Ascending);
               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  Religion@1000000000 : Record 59301;
                                  SumYear@1000000001 : Integer;
                                BEGIN
                                  CLEAR(ApplicantReligion);
                                  SeaServTotalYear := 0;
                                  SeaServTotalMonth := 0;
                                  SeaServTotalDay := 0;

                                  IF Religion.GET(Applicant."Religion Code") THEN
                                    ApplicantReligion := Religion.Description;

                                  CLEAR(ApplicantPictureTxt);
                                  IF Applicant.Picture.HASVALUE THEN
                                    Applicant.GetPicture(ApplicantPictureTxt);

                                  SeaServTotalYear := "Applicant Job History".GetTotalSeaTime(Applicant."No.", 0);
                                  SeaServTotalMonth := "Applicant Job History".GetTotalSeaTime(Applicant."No.", 1);
                                  SeaServTotalDay := "Applicant Job History".GetTotalSeaTime(Applicant."No.", 2);
                                END;

               DataItemLink=No.=FIELD(Applicant No.) }

    { 1000000048;2;Column;DateRegistered     ;

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

  DATASET
  {
    { 1000000000;;DataItem;                  ;
               DataItemTable=Table59025;
               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  GeneralLedgerSetup@1000000000 : Record 98;
                                BEGIN
                                  CurrencyCode := "Job Application"."Currency Code";
                                  IF CurrencyCode = '' THEN BEGIN
                                    GeneralLedgerSetup.GET;
                                    CurrencyCode := GeneralLedgerSetup."LCY Code";
                                  END;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=Line No.,Applicant No.,Status }

    { 1000000075;1;Column;JobApplicationLineNo;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Line No." }

    { 1000000001;1;Column;ApplicantNo        ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Applicant No." }

    { 1000000002;1;Column;PositionCode       ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Position Code" }

    { 1000000003;1;Column;Description        ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application".Description }

               SourceExpr=CurrencyCode }

                                 ORDER(Ascending);

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

OBJECT Report 59012 Letter of Guarantee
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=07/04/18;
    Time=[ 5:44:42 PM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 1000000000;;DataItem;                  ;
               DataItemTable=Table59025;
               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  Applicant@1000000000 : Record 59010;
                                  ApplicantQualifications@1000000001 : Record 59019;
                                  CountryRegion@1000000002 : Record 9;
                                BEGIN
                                  CLEAR(ApplicantFullName);
                                  CLEAR(ApplicantBirthDate);
                                  CLEAR(ApplicantPassportNo);
                                  CLEAR(ApplicantPassportExpDate);
                                  CLEAR(Nationality);
                                  "Job Application".CALCFIELDS(Vessel);

                                  IF Applicant.GET("Job Application"."Applicant No.") THEN BEGIN
                                    ApplicantFullName := Applicant.FullName;
                                    ApplicantBirthDate := Applicant."Birth Date";
                                    IF CountryRegion.GET(Applicant."Country/Region Code") THEN
                                      Nationality := CountryRegion.Name;
                                  END;

                                  ApplicantQualifications.RESET;
                                  ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE("Applicant No.", "Job Application"."Applicant No.");
                                  ApplicantQualifications.SETRANGE(Type, ApplicantQualifications.Type::Passport);
                                  IF ApplicantQualifications.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                    ApplicantPassportNo := ApplicantQualifications."Document No.";
                                    ApplicantPassportExpDate := ApplicantQualifications."To Date";
                                  END;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=Line No.,Applicant No.,Status }

    { 1000000075;1;Column;JobApplicationLineNo;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Line No." }

    { 1000000001;1;Column;ApplicantNo        ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Applicant No." }

    { 1000000002;1;Column;PositionCode       ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Position Code" }

    { 1000000003;1;Column;Description        ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application".Description }

    { 1000000004;1;Column;ApplicantFullName  ;
               SourceExpr=ApplicantFullName }

    { 1000000005;1;Column;ApplicantBirthDate ;
               SourceExpr=ApplicantBirthDate }

    { 1000000006;1;Column;ApplicantPassportNo;
               SourceExpr=ApplicantPassportNo }

    { 1000000007;1;Column;ApplicantPassportExpDate;
               SourceExpr=ApplicantPassportExpDate }

    { 1000000008;1;Column;SignOnDate         ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Sign-On Date" }

    { 1000000009;1;Column;DateOfDeparture    ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Date of Departure" }

    { 1000000010;1;Column;DepartureDetail1   ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Departure Details 1" }

    { 1000000011;1;Column;DepartureDetail2   ;
               SourceExpr="Job Application"."Departure Details 2" }

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

                              <KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether>
                              <Paragraphs>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value EvaluationMode="Auto">Seafarers Employment Agreement (SEA)</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontStyle>Italic</FontStyle>
                                        <FontSize>6pt</FontSize>
                                        <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                                        <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <SpaceBefore>2pt</SpaceBefore>
                                  <SpaceAfter>2pt</SpaceAfter>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value EvaluationMode="Auto">"A seafarer's employment agreement shall continue to have effect while the seafarer is held captive on or off ship as a result of acts of piracy or armed robbery against ships, regardless of whether the date fixed for its expiry has passed or either party has given notice to suspend or terminate it. For the purpose of this paragraph, the term:</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                                        <FontSize>6pt</FontSize>
                                        <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                                        <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <SpaceBefore>2pt</SpaceBefore>
                                  <SpaceAfter>0pt</SpaceAfter>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value EvaluationMode="Auto">a) piracy shall have the same meaning as in the United Nation Convention on the Law of the Sea, 1952;</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                                        <FontSize>6pt</FontSize>
                                        <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                                        <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <SpaceBefore>0pt</SpaceBefore>
                                  <SpaceAfter>0pt</SpaceAfter>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value EvaluationMode="Auto">b) armed robbery against ships means any illegal act of violence or detention or any act of depredation,  or threat thereof, other than an act of piracy, committed for private ends and directed against a ship or against persons or property on board such a ship, within a State's internal waters, archipelagic waters and territorial sea, or any act of inciting or intentionally facilitating an act described above."</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                                        <FontSize>6pt</FontSize>
                                        <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                                        <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <SpaceBefore>0pt</SpaceBefore>
                                  <SpaceAfter>2pt</SpaceAfter>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value EvaluationMode="Auto">Payment of Wages:</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontStyle>Italic</FontStyle>
                                        <FontSize>6pt</FontSize>
                                        <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                                        <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <SpaceBefore>2pt</SpaceBefore>
                                  <SpaceAfter>2pt</SpaceAfter>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value EvaluationMode="Auto">Where a sea farer is held captive on or off the ship as a result of acts of piracy or armed robbery against the ships, wages and other entitlements under the seafarer's employment aggreement, relevant collective bargaining agreement or applicable national laws, including the remittance of any allotments shall continue to be paid during the entire period of captivity and until the seafarer is released and duly repatriated in accordance with Standard A2.5.1 or, where the seafarer dies while in captivity, until the date of death as determined in accordance with applicable national laws or regulations. The terms piracy and armed robbery against ships shall have the same meaning as in Standard A2.1.</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                                        <FontSize>6pt</FontSize>
                                        <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                                        <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>

                                      <Value EvaluationMode="Auto">IV. B. Social Security, Protection Benefits and Medical Care</Value>
                                      <Style>

                                      <Value EvaluationMode="Auto">The employment of the Seafarer maybe deemed terminated under following conditions:
a)     when the seafarer signs-off due to shipwreck, ship's sale, lay-up of vessel, discontinuance of voyage of which under such
        condition the seafarer must have one (1) month basic compensation as termination pay
b)     when arrangements have been made for the seafarer to join another ship
c)     when the seafarer requests for early termination of his contract, he shall be liable for his repatriation cost as well as the
         transportation cost of his replacement. Notice of early termination of contract should be minimum one (1) month. The employer may,
         in case of compassionate grouds, assume the transportation cost of the seafarer's replacement but not limited to the following
         cases:

              c.1. Diagnose with severe illness of an immediate member of seafarer's family which includes his parents, spouse andchildren the seafarer is married or his parents if the seafarer is single.

              c.2. Incidence of death of an immediate member of seafarer's family which inludes his parents, spouse and children if the seafarer is married or his parents if the seafarer is single.

d)      when the seafarer commits the act of desertion or jump ships off the vessel,  he shall be penalized with dismissal and shall be liable to pay the cost of repatriation and his replacement.</Value>

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
