OBJECT Page 59036 Web Service Reset Password
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=07/04/18;
    Time=[ 5:53:37 AM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    DeleteAllowed=No;
    ModifyAllowed=No;
    SourceTable=Table99008535;
    PageType=Card;
    SourceTableTemporary=Yes;
    OnModifyRecord=VAR
                     UserProperty@1000000002 : Record 2000000121;
                     User@1000000000 : Record 2000000120;
                     IdentityManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 9801;
                     ErrInvalidOrExpiredToken@1000000004 : TextConst 'ENU=You have an invalid or expired password reset token.';
                     ErrPassword@1000000003 : TextConst 'ENU=Password must have a value.';
                     ErrConfirmPassword@1000000005 : TextConst 'ENU=Confirm Password must have a value.';
                     ErrPasswordStrength@1000000006 : TextConst 'ENU=The password that you entered does not meet the minimum requirements. It must be at least 8 characters long and contain at least one uppercase letter, one lowercase letter, and one number.';
                     ErrDisabledAccount@1000000007 : TextConst 'ENU=Your account has been disabled. Please contact your system administrator.';
                   BEGIN
                     IF Token = '' THEN
                       ERROR(ErrInvalidOrExpiredToken);

                     IF Password = '' THEN
                       ERROR(ErrPassword);

                     IF ConfirmPassword = '' THEN
                       ERROR(ErrConfirmPassword);

                     UserProperty.SETRANGE("WebServices Key", Token);
                     IF UserProperty. FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                       User.GET(UserProperty."User Security ID");
                       IF User.State = User.State::Disabled THEN
                         ERROR(ErrDisabledAccount);

                       //  Change the password
                       IF IdentityManagement.ValidatePasswordStrength(Password) THEN BEGIN
                         SETUSERPASSWORD(User."User Security ID", Password);
                         // Change the web service key / token
                         IdentityManagement.CreateWebServicesKeyNoExpiry(User."User Security ID");
                       END ELSE
                        ERROR(ErrPasswordStrength);
                     END ELSE
                       ERROR(ErrInvalidOrExpiredToken);
                   END;

  }
  CONTROLS
  {
    { 1000000000;0;Container;
                ContainerType=ContentArea }

    { 1000000001;1;Group  ;
                Name=General;
                GroupType=Group }

    { 1000000004;2;Field  ;
                Name=Token;
                SourceExpr=Token }

    { 1000000002;2;Field  ;
                Name=Password;
                SourceExpr=Password }

    { 1000000003;2;Field  ;
                Name=Confirm Password;
                SourceExpr=ConfirmPassword }

  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      Username@1000000002 : Text;
      Token@1000000003 : Text;
      Password@1000000001 : Text;
      ConfirmPassword@1000000000 : Text;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

OBJECT Page 59037 Web Service Key Validator
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=07/03/18;
    Time=[ 5:53:03 PM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    Permissions=TableData 2000000120=r,
                TableData 2000000121=rm;
    DeleteAllowed=No;
    ModifyAllowed=No;
    SourceTable=Table99008535;
    PageType=Card;
    SourceTableTemporary=Yes;
    OnModifyRecord=VAR
                     User@1000000000 : Record 2000000120;
                     UserProperty@1000000002 : Record 2000000121;
                     IdentityManagement@1000000001 : Codeunit 9801;
                   BEGIN
                      IF Token = '' THEN
                       ERROR(ErrInvalidToken);

                     UserProperty.SETCURRENTKEY("WebServices Key");
                     UserProperty.SETRANGE("WebServices Key", Token);
                     IF UserProperty.COUNT > 1 THEN
                       ERROR(ErrDuplicateToken, Token);

                     IF UserProperty.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                       User.GET(UserProperty."User Security ID");
                       Username := User."User Name";
                     END ELSE
                       ERROR(ErrInvalidOrExpiredToken);
                   END;

  }
  CONTROLS
  {
    { 1000000000;0;Container;
                ContainerType=ContentArea }

    { 1000000001;1;Group  ;
                Name=General;
                GroupType=Group }

    { 1000000002;2;Field  ;
                Name=Username;
                SourceExpr=Username;
                Editable=FALSE }

    { 1000000003;2;Field  ;
                Name=Token;
                SourceExpr=Token }

  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      Username@1000000000 : Text;
      Token@1000000001 : Text;
      ErrDuplicateToken@1000000002 : TextConst 'ENU=Token %1 has caused an error to the user credential. Please contact your administrator.';
      ErrInvalidToken@1000000003 : TextConst 'ENU=You have an invalid password reset token.';
      ErrInvalidOrExpiredToken@1000000004 : TextConst 'ENU=You have an invalid or expired password reset token.';

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}

               END;

    OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                       NoteTxt := GetNote;
                     END;

  }
  CONTROLS
  {
    { 1000000000;0;Container;
                ContainerType=ContentArea }

    { 1000000001;1;Group  ;
                Name=Group;
                GroupType=Repeater }

    { 1000000002;2;Field  ;
                SourceExpr="Line No." }

    { 1000000003;2;Field  ;
                SourceExpr="Table ID" }

    { 1000000004;2;Field  ;
                SourceExpr="No." }

    { 1000000007;2;Field  ;
                SourceExpr="User ID" }

    { 1000000008;2;Field  ;
                SourceExpr="To User ID" }

    { 1000000005;2;Field  ;
                Name=Note;
                SourceExpr=NoteTxt;
                OnValidate=BEGIN
                             SetNote(NoteTxt);
                           END;
                            }

    { 1000000006;2;Field  ;
                SourceExpr=Created;
                Visible=FALSE }

    { 1000000009;2;Field  ;
                SourceExpr=Modified;
                Visible=FALSE }

  }
  CODE

OBJECT Page 59900 User Role
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=07/15/18;
    Time=[ 5:35:33 AM];
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=ATLAS01.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    InsertAllowed=No;
    DeleteAllowed=No;
    ModifyAllowed=No;
    SourceTable=Table2000000053;
    DelayedInsert=Yes;
    PageType=ListPart;
    OnOpenPage=BEGIN
                 FILTERGROUP(2);
                 SETRANGE("User Security ID", USERSECURITYID);
                 FILTERGROUP(1);
               END;

    OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                       IF User."User Name" <> '' THEN
                         CurrPage.CAPTION := User."User Name";
                       PermissionEditable := ISNULLGUID("App ID");
                     END;

    OnNewRecord=BEGIN
                  IF User.GET("User Security ID") THEN;
                  PermissionEditable := ISNULLGUID("App ID");
                  CALCFIELDS("App Name","Role Name");
                END;

    OnInsertRecord=BEGIN
                     User.TESTFIELD("User Name");
                     PermissionEditable := ISNULLGUID("App ID");
                     CALCFIELDS("App Name","Role Name");
                   END;

    OnModifyRecord=BEGIN
                     PermissionEditable := ISNULLGUID("App ID");
                     CALCFIELDS("App Name","Role Name");
                   END;

    OnDeleteRecord=VAR
                     UserGroupAccessControl@1000 : Record 9002;
                   BEGIN
                     UserGroupAccessControl.SETFILTER("User Group Code",'<>%1','');
                     UserGroupAccessControl.SETRANGE("User Security ID","User Security ID");
                     UserGroupAccessControl.SETRANGE("Role ID","Role ID");
                     UserGroupAccessControl.SETRANGE("Company Name","Company Name");
                     IF UserGroupAccessControl.FINDFIRST THEN
                       ERROR(InUserGroupErr,UserGroupAccessControl."User Group Code");
                     PermissionEditable := ISNULLGUID("App ID");
                   END;

    ActionList=ACTIONS
    {
      { 7       ;    ;ActionContainer;
                      Name=PermissionActions;
                      ActionContainerType=ActionItems }
      { 9       ;1   ;Action    ;
                      Name=Permissions;
                      ShortCutKey=Shift+Ctrl+p;
                      CaptionML=ENU=Permissions;
                      RunObject=Page 9803;
                      RunPageLink=Role ID=FIELD(Role ID);
                      Enabled=PermissionEditable;
                      Image=Permission }
      { 8       ;1   ;Action    ;
                      CaptionML=ENU=Permission Sets;
                      RunObject=Page 9802;
                      Image=ListPage }
    }
  }
  CONTROLS
  {
    { 1   ;0   ;Container ;
                ContainerType=ContentArea }

    { 2   ;1   ;Group     ;
                Name=Group;
                CaptionML=ENU=User Permissions;
                GroupType=Repeater }

    { 10  ;2   ;Field     ;
                SourceExpr="User Name";
                Visible=FALSE }

    { 3   ;2   ;Field     ;
                Name=<Permission Set>;
                CaptionML=ENU=Permission Set;
                SourceExpr="Role ID";
                OnValidate=VAR
                             AggregatePermissionSet@1000 : Record 2000000167;
                           BEGIN
                             // If the user used the lookup, skip validation
                             IF SkipValidation THEN BEGIN
                               SkipValidation := FALSE;
                               EXIT;
                             END;

                             // Get the Scope and App ID for a matching Role ID
                             AggregatePermissionSet.SETRANGE("Role ID","Role ID");
                             AggregatePermissionSet.FINDFIRST;

                             IF AggregatePermissionSet.COUNT > 1 THEN
                               ERROR(MultipleRoleIDErr,"Role ID");

                             Scope := AggregatePermissionSet.Scope;
                             "App ID" := AggregatePermissionSet."App ID";

                             CALCFIELDS("App Name","Role Name");

                             SkipValidation := FALSE; // re-enable validation
                           END;

                OnLookup=VAR
                           PermissionSetLookupRecord@1002 : Record 2000000167;
                           PermissionSetLookup@1001 : Page 9841;
                         BEGIN
                           PermissionSetLookup.LOOKUPMODE := TRUE;
                           IF PermissionSetLookup.RUNMODAL = ACTION::LookupOK THEN BEGIN
                             PermissionSetLookup.GETRECORD(PermissionSetLookupRecord);
                             Scope := PermissionSetLookupRecord.Scope;
                             "App ID" := PermissionSetLookupRecord."App ID";
                             "Role ID" := PermissionSetLookupRecord."Role ID";
                             CALCFIELDS("App Name","Role Name");
                             SkipValidation := TRUE;
                           END;
                         END;
                          }

    { 4   ;2   ;Field     ;
                Name=<Description>;
                DrillDown=No;
                CaptionML=ENU=Description;
                SourceExpr="Role Name";
                Editable=FALSE }

  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      User@1000 : Record 2000000120;
      InUserGroupErr@1001 : TextConst '@@@="%1=a user group code, e.g. ADMIN or SALESDEPT";ENU=You cannot remove this permission set because it is included in user group %1.';
      PermissionEditable@1002 : Boolean;
      MultipleRoleIDErr@1003 : TextConst '@@@=%1 will be replaced with a Role ID code value from the Permission Set table;ENU=The permission set %1 is defined multiple times in this context. Use the lookup button to select the relevant permission set.';
      SkipValidation@1004 : Boolean;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }
}
